quran[842]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,Ndahiriye (ku bamalayika bahagaze) ku mirongo itunganye (basenga)
  37,2,No ku (bamalayika) bajyana ibicu (babyerekeza aho Allah ashaka)
  37,3,No ku (bamalayika) basoma (amagambo ya Allah) basingiza (Nyagasani wabo)
  37,4,"Mu by’ukuri, Imana yanyu ni imwe"
  37,5,"Nyagasani w’ibirere n’isi ndetse n’ibiri hagati ya byo, akaba na Nyagasani w’uburasirazuba bwose"
  37,6,"Mu by’ukuri, ikirere cyegereye isi twagitakishije inyenyeri"
  37,7,Tunakirinda buri shitani ryose ryigometse (dukoresheje ibishashi by’umuriro)
  37,8,"Ntirishobora kumviriza (ibivugwa n’abamalayika) mu ijuru, kubera ko riterwa (ibishashi) mu mpande zose"
  37,9,Bigamije kuryirukana. Kandi (no ku munsi w’imperuka) rizahanishwa ibihano bihoraho
  37,10,Usibye iribashije kwiba (ibanga) bwangu nuko rigakurikizwa ibishashi by’umuriro
  37,11,Ngaho (yewe Muhamadi) babaze (abahakanyi b’i Maka) niba iremwa ryabo ari ryo rikomeye kurusha ibyo twaremye (ibirere n’isi ndetse n’imisozi). Mu by’ukuri twabaremye mu ibumba rimatira
  37,12,Ahubwo uratangazwa (no kuba bahakana izuka) ndetse banannyega (ubutumwa bwawe)
  37,13,N’iyo bibukijwe (amagambo ya Allah) ntacyo bibamarira
  37,14,N’ iyo babonye igitangaza (giturutse kwa Allah) baragisuzugura
  37,15,"Maze bakavuga bati \"Iki si ikindi usibye ko ari uburozi bugaragara"
  37,16,Ese nidupfa tugahinduka igitaka ndetse n’amagufa (akabora) tuzazurwa koko
  37,17,N’abakurambere bacu (bazazurwa) se
  37,18,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Yego muzazurwa, kandi muzaba musuzuguritse"
  37,19,"Mu by’ukuri, impanda izavuzwa rimwe, maze (bazurwe) babone (ibyo basezeranijwe)"
  37,20,"Nuko bavuge bati \"Mbega ishyano tubonye ! Uyu ni umunsi w’ibarura n’ibihembo"
  37,21,Uyu ni wo munsi w’urubanza mwajyaga muhinyura
  37,22,"(Abamalayika bazababwira) bati \"Mukoranye inkozi z’ibibi n’abambari bazo ndetse n’ibyo basengaga"
  37,23,"Bitari Allah, maze muberekeze mu nzira ibaganisha mu muriro ugurumana"
  37,24,"Munabahagarike kuko mu by’ukuri, bagomba (kubanza) kubazwa"
  37,25,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Byagenze bite ko mudatabarana (nk’uko mwabigenzaga ) ku isi"
  37,26,Ahubwo kuri uwo munsi bazaba baciye bugufi (basuzuguritse)
  37,27,Nuko bamwe bahindukirirane abandi babazanye
  37,28,"Bavuga bati \"Mu by’ukuri, ni mwe mwatugeragaho muduhatira ubuyobe"
  37,29,"Babasubize bati \"Ahubwo ntabwo mwari abemeramana"
  37,30,Kandi nta bubasha twari tubafiteho; ahubwo mwari abantu barengera (imbibi za Allah)
  37,31,None ijambo (ry’ibihano) rya Nyagasani wacu ridusohoreyeho ko mu by’ukuri (tugomba) gusogongera (ibihano)
  37,32,"Twarabayobeje kuko mu by’ukuri, natwe twari twarayobye"
  37,33,Kuri uwo munsi bose bazaba bafatanyije ibihano
  37,34,"Mu by’ukuri, uko ni ko tugenza inkozi z’ibibi"
  37,35,"Kuko iyo babwirwaga ko nta yindi mana ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri uretse Allah, baribonaga"
  37,36,"Bakanavuga bati \"Ese koko tureke imana zacu kubera umusizi w’umusazi"
  37,37,Ahubwo (Intumwa Muhamadi ) yazanye ukuri inahamya intumwa (zayibanjirije)
  37,38,"Mu by’ukuri, mwe (ababangikanyamana ) mugiye gusogongera ibihano bibabaza"
  37,39,Kandi nta kindi muri buhemberwe kitari ibyo mwakoreye
  37,40,Uretse abagaragu ba Allah b’imbonera
  37,41,Abo bazahabwa amafunguro azwi (mu ijuru)
  37,42,Imbuto; kandi bazaba bubashywe
  37,43,Mu busitani bwuje inema (Ijuru)
  37,44,Bari ku bitanda berekeranye
  37,45,Bazengurutswamo ibirahuri by’ibinyobwa byiza
  37,46,"Byererana, biryoheye ababinywa"
  37,47,Nta ngaruka bizabagiraho ndetse nta n’ubwo bizatuma bata ubwenge
  37,48,"Kandi bazaba bafite abagore biyubashye, b’amaso meza manini"
  37,49,Bameze nk’amagi yarinzwe neza
  37,50,Maze bamwe bahindukire barebe abandi babazanye
  37,51,"Umwe muri bo azavuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, nari mfite inshuti magara (ku isi)"
  37,52,"Yajyaga ivuga iti \"Ese wowe koko uri mu bemera (izuka)"
  37,53,"Ese nidupfa tugahinduka igitaka n’amagufwa (akabora), tuzabazwa ibyo twakoze koko"
  37,54,"Avuge ati \"Ese mushobora kureba (mu muriro)"
  37,55,Nuko arebe amubone hagati mu muriro ugurumana
  37,56,"Avuge ati \"Ndahiye ku izina rya Allah! Wari hafi yo kunyobya"
  37,57,"Iyo bitaza kuba ku bw’ingabire ya Nyagasani wanjye, nanjye nari kuba mu bazanywe (mu muriro kimwe nawe)"
  37,58,"(Abazaba bari mu ijuru bazavuga bati)\"Ese ntabwo tuzongera gupfa"
  37,59,"Usibye gusa urupfu rwacu rwa mbere, ndetse nta n’ubwo tuzahanwa (nyuma y’uko twinjiye mu ijuru)"
  37,60,"Mu by’ukuri, iyi ni intsinzi ihambaye"
  37,61,"Ku bw’ibyo, ngaho abakora (ibyiza) nibakore"
  37,62,"Ese kwakirwa gutyo niko kwiza, cyangwa (kwakirizwa) igiti cya cya Zaqum(ni byo byiza)"
  37,63,"Mu by’ukuri, (icyo giti ) twakigize ikigeragezo ku bahakanyi"
  37,64,Ni igiti gishibuka mu ndiba y’umuriro ugurumana
  37,65,Imbuto zacyo zimeze nk’imitwe y’amashitani
  37,66,"Mu by’ukuri, bazazirya bazuzuze inda"
  37,67,Maze barenzeho uruvange rw’amazi yatuye
  37,68,Hanyuma igarukiro ryabo rizabe mu muriro ugurumana
  37,69,"Mu by’ukuri, basanze abakurambere babo barayobye"
  37,70,Nuko nabo bihutira kugera ikirenge mu cyabo
  37,71,Kandi rwose abenshi mu babayeho mbere yabo barayobye
  37,72,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, twaranaboherereje ababurizi"
  37,73,Ngaho reba uko iherezo ry’ababuriwe ryagenze
  37,74,Uretse abagaragu ba Allah b’imbonera
  37,75,"Mu by’ukuri, Nuhu yaratwiyamabaje kandi ni twe beza bo kwiyambazwa"
  37,76,Nuko tumurokorana n’abantu be mu makuba ahambaye
  37,77,Maze dusigaza abamukomokaho
  37,78,Tunamuha kuzasigara avugwa neza mu bazabaho nyuma ye
  37,79,Amahoro ni abe kuri Nuhu mu biremwa byose
  37,80,"Mu by’ukuri, uko ni ko tugororera abakoze neza"
  37,81,"Mu by’ukuri, yari umwe mu bagaragu bacu b’abemeramana (twarokoye)"
  37,82,Hanyuma turoha abandi (bahakanye)
  37,83,"Mu by’ukuri, no mu bamukurikije harimo Ibrahimu"
  37,84,Ubwo yaganaga Nyagasani we n’umutima ukeye
  37,85,"Ubwo yabwiraga se n’abantu be ati \"Ibi musenga ni ibiki"
  37,86,Ese murashaka gusenga ibigirwamana mwihimbiye muretse Allah
  37,87,Ese mutekereza iki kuri Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose
  37,88,Nuko ( Ibrahimu ) yitegereza inyenyeri
  37,89,"Maze aravuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, njye ndarwaye\" (Ibyo yabikoze ari amayeri yo kugira ngo asigare aho basengeraga ibigirwamana byabo kugira ngo abijanjagure, ndetse no kugira ngo atajyana nabo mu mihango yabo ya gipagani)"
  37,90,Nuko barahindukira barigendera
  37,91,"Maze yinyabya ku bigirwamana byabo, nuko aravuga ati \"Ese ntimurya (aya mafunguro mwateguriwe)"
  37,92,Bite byanyu ko mutavuga
  37,93,Maze arabyadukira abijanjaguza ukuboko kwe kw’iburyo
  37,94,Nuko (ba babangikanyamana) bagaruka bamugana bihuta
  37,95,"Arababwira ati \"Ese musenga ibyo mwihangiye"
  37,96,"Kandi Allah yarabaremye, mwe n’ibyo mwikorera"
  37,97,"Baravuga bati \"Nimumwubakire itanura maze mumujugunye mu muriro ugurumana"
  37,98,"Bamucuriye umugambi mubisha, nuko turabasuzuguza"
  37,99,"Nuko (amaze kurokoka umuriro) aravuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, ngannye kwa Nyagasani wanjye, azanyobora"
  37,100,Nyagasani wanjye! Mpa (umwana ) uzaba umwe mu ntungane
  37,101,Nuko tumuha inkuru nziza yo (kuzabyara) umuhungu witonda (ari we Isimayili)
  37,102,"Maze (umuhungu we) amaze kugera aho bagendana, (ise) aravuga ati \"Mwana wanjye! Mu by’ukuri, narose nkubaga (ngutangaho igitambo kwa Allah), mbwira uko ubibona?\" Aravuga ati \"Dawe! Kora icyo wategetswe, Allah nabishaka uzansanga mu bihangana"
  37,103,"Nuko bombi bamaze kumvira (itegeko rya Allah), (Ibrahimu) amuryamisha hasi yubitse umutwe (kugira ngo amubage)"
  37,104,"Maze turamuhamagara tuti \"Yewe Ibrahimu"
  37,105,"Rwose wakabije inzozi. Mu by’ukuri, uko ni ko duhemba abakora neza"
  37,106,"Mu by’ukuri, iki ni cyo kigeragezo kigaragara"
  37,107,Nuko tumucunguza igitambo gihambaye (intama)
  37,108,Tunamuha kuzasigara avugwa neza mubazabaho nyuma ye
  37,109,Amahoro ni abe kuri Ibrahimu
  37,110,Uko ni ko tugorerera abakoze neza
  37,111,"Mu by’ukuri, (Ibrahimu) yari umwe mu bagaragu bacu b’abemera"
  37,112,"Kandi twamuhaye inkuru nziza (yo kuzabyara) Isihaka, akaba umuhanuzi (ndetse akaba n’umwe) mu ntungane"
  37,113,Nuko we na Isihaka tubaha imigisha. No mu rubyaro rwabo harimo abakora ibyiza ndetse n’abihemukira ku buryo bugaragara
  37,114,Kandi rwose Musa na Haruna twabahaye ingabire (y’ubutumwa)
  37,115,Maze tubarokorana n’abantu babo amakuba ahambaye (yo kurohama)
  37,116,Turanabatabara nuko baba ari bo batsinda
  37,117,Nuko tubaha igitabo (Tawurati) gisobanutse
  37,118,Tunabayobora inzira igororotse
  37,119,Kandi twanabahaye kuzasigara bavugwa neza mu bazabaho nyuma yabo
  37,120,Amahoro nabe kuri Musa na Haruna
  37,121,"Mu by’ukuri, uko ni ko tugororera abakoze neza"
  37,122,Rwose bombi bari mu bagaragu bacu b’abemera
  37,123,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, Iliyasi yari umwe mu ntumwa"
  37,124,"Ubwo yabwiraga abantu be ati \"Ese ntimutinya (Allah)"
  37,125,Ese musenga (ikigirwamana) Ba’ala muretse Umuremyi uhebuje
  37,126,"Allah, Nyagasani wanyu akaba na Nyagasani w’abakurambere banyu"
  37,127,"Nuko (Iliyasi) baramuhinyura. Mu by’ukuri, bazazanwa (kugira ngo bahanwe)"
  37,128,Uretse abagaragu ba Allah b’imbonera
  37,129,Twanamuhaye kuzasigara avugwa neza mu bazabaho nyuma ye
  37,130,Amahoro nabe kuri Iliyasi n’ab’iwe
  37,131,"Mu by’ukuri, uko ni ko tugororera abakoze neza"
  37,132,Mu by’ukuri (Iliyasi) yari umwe mu bagaragu bacu b’abemera
  37,133,Kandi rwose Lutwi yari umwe mu ntumwa
  37,134,Ubwo twamurokoranaga n’ab’iwe bose
  37,135,Usibye gusa umukecuru (umugore we) wabaye mubasigaye (mu bihano)
  37,136,Hanyuma abandi (bo mu mudugudu wa Sodoma) turabarimbura
  37,137,Kandi rwose mubanyuraho (ku matongo yabo) mu gitondo
  37,138,Ndetse na nijoro. Ese ntimutekereza
  37,139,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, Yunusu yari umwe mu ntumwa"
  37,140,Wibuke ubwo yahungiraga mu bwato bwuzuye (abantu n’ibintu)
  37,141,"Maze (akemera) kuba umwe mu batombora (kugira ngo bamenye urohwa mu nyanja), nuko aratsindwa (aba ari we uyirohwamo)"
  37,142,Nuko ifi iramumira kuko yari yakoze igikorwa kigayitse (cyo gusiga abantu be atabiherewe uburenganzira na Allah)
  37,143,Iyo ataza kuba ari umwe mu basingiza Allah
  37,144,Yari kuguma mu nda yayo kugeza ku munsi (abantu) bazazurirwaho
  37,145,Ariko twamujugunye ku nkombe ameze nk’umurwayi
  37,146,Maze dutegeka ko (aho yari ari) hamera uruyuzi rwera ibihaza kugira ngo ajye abirya
  37,147,Nuko tumwohereza ku bantu ibihumbi ijana cyangwa banarenga
  37,148,"Maze baremera, nuko tubaha umunezero w’igihe gito"
  37,149,"Ngaho (yewe Muhamadi) babaze uti \"Ese Nyagasani wawe afite abakobwa gusa, hanyuma bo bakagira abahungu"
  37,150,Cyangwa twaremye abamalayika b’abakobwa babireba (ikaba ari yo mpamvu bavuga ko abamalayika ari igitsina gore)
  37,151,"Mu by’ukuri, no mu binyoma byabo (ababangikanyamana b’i Maka) baravuga (bati)"
  37,152,"Allah yarabyaye (bavugaga ko abamalayika ari abakobwa ba Allah)\" Nyamara rwose ni abanyabinyoma"
  37,153,Nonese (ni ukubera iki) yaba yarahisemo abakobwa mu kimbo cy’abahungu
  37,154,Ese mwabaye mute? Amahitamo yanyu ashingira kuki
  37,155,Ese ntimutekereza
  37,156,Cyangwa mufite ibimenyetso bigaragara
  37,157,"Ngaho nimuzane igitabo cyanyu, niba muri abanyakuri"
  37,158,"Kandi banashyize isano hagati ye (Allah) n’amajini, nyamara amajini yo azi neza ko azazanwa (imbere ya Allah kugira ngo acirwe urubanza)"
  37,159,"Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Allah, ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamwitirira"
  37,160,Uretse abagaragu ba Allah b’imbonera (ni bo batajya bagira ibyo bamwitirira)
  37,161,"Bityo, mu by’ukuri mwe (ababangikanyamana) ndetse n’ibyo musenga bitari Allah"
  37,162,Nta n’umwe (mu bemeramana) mushobora kuyobya
  37,163,Uretse abazajya mu muriro ugurumana
  37,164,Kandi nta n’umwe muri twe (abamalayika) udafite umwanya uzwi (mu ijuru)
  37,165,"Mu by’ukuri, twe (abamalayika) dutonda imirongo (dusenga nk’uko Abayislamu babigenza)"
  37,166,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, ni twe dusingiza (Allah)"
  37,167,"(Kandi mu by’ukuri, ababangikanyamana b’i Maka) bajyaga bavuga bati"
  37,168,Iyo tuza kugira urwibutso nk’urw’abo hambere (mbere y’uko intumwa Muhamadi ihabwa ubutumwa)
  37,169,Mu by’ukuri twari kuba abagaragu ba Allah b’imbonera
  37,170,Nyamara (nyuma y’uko Qor’an ibagezeho) barayihakanye kandi vuba aha bazamenya (ukuri)
  37,171,"Kandi rwose, isezerano ryacu ryaje mbere ku bagaragu bacu b’intumwa"
  37,172,"Ko mu by’ukuri, ari bo bazatsinda"
  37,173,"Kandi ko mu by’ukuri, ingabo zacu ari zo zizatsinda"
  37,174,Bityo rero (yewe Muhamadi) birengagizeho igihe gito
  37,175,"Unabahozeho ijisho, kuko bidatinze bazabona (ibihano)"
  37,176,Ese ibihano byacu ni byo bashaka kwihutisha
  37,177,"Bityo, ubwo bizamanukira hafi yabo, kizaba ari igitondo kibi kuri babandi baburiwe"
  37,178,"Bityo, birengagize igihe gito (yewe Muhamadi)"
  37,179,"Unabahozeho ijisho, kuko bidatinze bazabona (ibihano)"
  37,180,"Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Nyagasani wawe, Nyagasani Nyiricyubahiro! Ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamwitirira"
  37,181,Kandi amahoro nabe ku ntumwa
  37,182,"Kandi ishimwe n’ikuzo byuzuye ni ibya Allah, Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose"
  38,1,Swad111! Ndahiriye kuri Qur’an yuje urwibutso
  38,2,Nyamara abahakanye bari mu bwibone n’ubwigomeke
  38,3,"Ese ni ibisekuru bingahe tworetse mbere yabo, bigatakamba by’impitagihe"
  38,4,"(Abarabu b’ababangikanya-mana) batangajwe no kugerwaho n’umuburizi (Muhamadi) ubakomokamo. Nuko abahakanyi baravuga bati \"Uyu ni umurozi w’umubeshyi"
  38,5,"Ese arashaka ko imana (zacu) zose ziba Imana imwe? Mu by’ ukuri, iki ni ikintu gitangaje"
  38,6,"Maze ibikomerezwa muri bo bigenda bivuga biti \"Nimugende munambe ku mana zanyu. Mu by’ukuri, uyu ni umugambi wateguwe"
  38,7,Ibi ntitwigeze tubyumva mu myizerere yo hambere. Ibi nta kindi biri cyo usibye kuba ari ibihimbano
  38,8,"Ese ni we wenyine muri twe waba warahishuriwe urwibutso? Ahubwo barashidikanya ku rwibutso rwanjye (Qur’an), kuko batarasogongera ku bihano byanjye"
  38,9,"Ese baba bafite ibigega by’impuhwe za Nyagasani wawe, Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Ugaba bihebuje"
  38,10,"Cyangwa baba bafite ubwami bw’ibirere n’isi ndetse n’ibiri hagati yabyo? Niba ari uko bimeze, ngaho nibazamuke mu kirere bakoresheje uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose (maze bakumire ubutumwa)"
  38,11,Izo ni ingabo zizatsindwa (nk’uko) iz’udutsiko zatsinzwe (mbere)
  38,12,"Mbere yabo (hari benshi) bahinyuye (intumwa); nk’abantu ba Nuhu, aba Adi ndetse na Farawo wari ufite inyubako zitangaje"
  38,13,"N’aba Thamudu, abantu ba Lutwi ndetse n’aba Ayikat (b’i Mediyani), bose bari udutsiko"
  38,14,"Nta na kamwe muri two katahinyuye intumwa, nuko ibihano byanjye biba impamo"
  38,15,Aba nta kindi bategereje kitari urusaku rumwe rudasubira
  38,16,"Kandi baravuga bati \"Nyagasani wacu! Twihutishirize ibyo watugeneye (ibihano) mbere y’uko umunsi w’ibarura ugera"
  38,17,"Ihanganire ibyo bavuga (yewe Muhamadi), kandi wibuke umugaragu wacu Dawudi wari umunyembaraga (mu kutugaragira). Mu by’ukuri, yicuzaga kuri Allah cyane"
  38,18,"Mu by’ukuri, twashoboje imisozi gufatanya nawe (Dawudi) kudusingiza buri uko bucyeye n’uko bwije"
  38,19,"Ndetse n’inyoni zikusanyirijwe hamwe, zaramwumviye (zifatanya nawe mu kudusingiza)"
  38,20,"Maze dukomeza ubwami bwe, tunamuha ubushishozi no guca imanza neza"
  38,21,"Ese (yewe Muhamadi) inkuru y’abari bashyamiranye yaba yarakugezeho, ubwo buriraga bagasanga (Dawudi) aho yasengeraga (Mih’rab)"
  38,22,"Ubwo binjiraga kwa Dawudi maze akabikanga, bakavuga bati \"Wigira ubwoba! Twembi twashyamiranye; umwe muri twe yahuguje undi. Bityo, dukiranure mu kuri kandi ntubogame, ndetse unatuyobore inzira igororotse"
  38,23,"Mu by’ukuri, uyu muvandimwe wanjye afite intama mirongo cyenda n’icyenda, mu gihe njye mfite intama imwe (gusa), ariko yavuze ati \"Nayo yindagize!\" (Nyamara njye simbishaka), none yandushije ijwi"
  38,24,"(Dawudi atabanje kumva undi) aravuga ati \"Rwose yaguhuguje kuba yagusabye intama yawe ngo ayongere mu ze. Kandi mu by’ukuri, abenshi mu bafatanyije imitungo barahuguzanya, uretse babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza; kandi ni bo bake\". Nuko Dawudi amenya ko twamugerageje asaba imbabazi Nyagasani we, yitura hasi yubamye, anicuza (kuri Allah)"
  38,25,"Nuko ibyo turabimubabarira. Kandi mu by’ukuri, ari hafi yacu ndetse azagira igarukiro ryiza (Ijuru)"
  38,26,"Yewe Dawudi! Mu by’ukuri, twakugize umusigire ku isi, bityo jya ukiranura abantu mu kuri kandi ntuzagendere ku marangamutima, kugira ngo atazavaho akuyobya inzira ya Allah. Mu by’ukuri, abazayoba inzira ya Allah bazahanishwa ibihano bikaze, kubera kwibagirwa umunsi w’ibarura"
  38,27,"Ntitwanaremye ikirere n’isi ndetse n’ibiri hagati ya byo nta mpamvu. Uko ni ko abahakanye bibwira. Bityo, ibihano bikaze by’umuriro bizaba ku bahakanyi"
  38,28,Ese abemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza twabafata kimwe n’abangizi ku isi? Cyangwa se ngo dufate kimwe abatinya Imana n’inkozi z’ibibi
  38,29,"Iki ni igitabo cyuje imigisha twaguhishuriye (yewe Muhamadi), kugira ngo (abantu) batekereze ku mirongo yacyo ndetse no kugira ngo abanyabwenge bibuke"
  38,30,"Kandi Dawudi twamuhaye Sulayimani nk’impano. Yari umugaragu mwiza. Mu by’ukuri, yicuzaga kuri Allah cyane"
  38,31,(Ibuka) ubwo nimugoroba yamurikirwaga amafarasi y’ubwoko bwiza kandi yiruka cyane
  38,32,"Nuko akavuga ati \"Nakunze iby’isi kugeza ubwo nibagirwa Nyagasani wanjye, izuba ririnda rirenga"
  38,33,"Ngaho nimuzingarurire!\" Maze atangira kuzagaza ku maguru no ku majosi"
  38,34,"Kandi rwose twagerageje Sulayimani tujugunya ikibiri112 ku ntebe ye y’ubwami, (bimutera gusa nk’utakaje ubwami bwe, abona ko yageragejwe) nyuma yicuza ku Mana"
  38,35,"Aravuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye! Mbabarira, unangabire ubwami butazigera buhabwa undi nyuma yanjye. Mu by’ukuri, ni wowe ugaba bihebuje"
  38,36,"Nuko dutegeka umuyaga guca bugufi ku itegeko rye, akawerekeza aho ashaka (kujya hose)"
  38,37,Ndetse n’amashitani y’amoko yose; yaba ayubaka n’ayibira mu mazi (twayategetse kumwumvira)
  38,38,Naho andi (yamwigomekagaho) yayafungaga ku minyururu
  38,39,"(Allah abwira Sulayimani ati) \"Ibi ni impano yacu; bityo ha (uwo ushatse) cyangwa wime (uwo ushatse), nta cyo uzabazwa"
  38,40,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, yari hafi yacu ndetse azagira igarukiro ryiza (Ijuru)"
  38,41,"Unibuke ubwo umugaragu wacu Ayubu yatakambiraga Nyagasani we agira ati \"Mu by’ukuri, Shitani yanteje ibyago n’ububabare"
  38,42,"(Allah aramubwira ati) \"Kubita ikirenge cyawe hasi; ayo mazi akonje (avuyemo) ni ayo kwiyuhagira no kunywa"
  38,43,"Nuko k’ubwimpuhwe ziduturutseho, tumugarurira umuryango we uri kumwe n’abandi nkawo, kugira ngo bibe urwibutso ku banyabwenge"
  38,44,"Unafate umuba w’udushari mu kuboko kwawe maze uwukubitishe (umugore wawe113), kugira ngo udatatira indahiro. Mu by’ukuri, twasanze (Ayubu) ari umuntu wihangana akaba n’umugaragu mwiza, kandi rwose yicuzaga cyane (kuri Allah)"
  38,45,"Kandi wibuke (yewe Muhamadi) abagaragu bacu; Ibrahimu, Isihaka na Yakubu; bari abanyamurava (mu kudusenga) bakanagira ubushishozi (mu idini)"
  38,46,"Mu by’ukuri, twarabatoranyije tubaha umwihariko wo kwibuka imperuka"
  38,47,Kandi rwose imbere yacu bari intoranywa bakaba n’abantu beza
  38,48,"Unibuke Isimayili, Aliyasa na Dhul’kifli; bose bari abantu beza"
  38,49,"Iyi (Qur’an) ni urwibutso. Kandi mu by’ukuri, abatinya (Allah) bazagira igarukiro ryiza"
  38,50,"Ijuru rihoraho, bazafungurirwa imiryango yaryo"
  38,51,"Aho bazaba begamye, batumiza imbuto nyinshi n’ibinyobwa"
  38,52,Bazaba bari kumwe n’abagore barangamiye abagabo babo (gusa) kandi b’urungano
  38,53,Ibyo ni byo (bihembo) by’umunsi w’ibarura mwasezeranyijwe
  38,54,"Mu by’ukuri, ibyo ni amafunguro yacu adateze kuzashira"
  38,55,Ibyo (ni byo bizagororerwa abemera). Naho abanyabyaha bazagira igarukiro ribi
  38,56,"Umuriro wa Jahanamu bazinjiramo, ukazaba ari bwo buturo bubi"
  38,57,"Ibyo (ni byo bihano bazahanishwa). Bityo, nibabisogongere; ni amazi yatuye n’amashyira"
  38,58,N’ibindi (bihano) bimeze nkabyo by’ingeri nyinshi
  38,59,"(Abayobeje abandi bazabwirwa bati) \"Aka ni agatsiko kaje kubana namwe (mu muriro)\", (bavuge bati) \"Nta heza bashyikiye kuko mu by’ukuri, binjiye mu muriro"
  38,60,"(Abayobejwe) bazavuga bati \"Ahubwo ni mwe mutashyikiye aheza kuko ari mwe mwawudukururiye (umuriro); kandi ni cyo cyicaro kibi"
  38,61,"Bazavuga bati \"Nyagasani wacu! Uwadukururiye ibi mwongerere ibihano byo mu muriro byikubye kabiri"
  38,62,"Bazanavuga bati \"Byatugendekeye bite ko tutabona bamwe mu bantu twabaraga mu nkozi z’ibibi"
  38,63,"Ese twabibeshyagaho (ku isi) tubannyega (naho ari abantu b’intungane, cyangwa bari kumwe natwe mu muriro) amaso yacu akaba atababona"
  38,64,"Mu by’ukuri, uko gusubiranamo kw’abantu bo mu muriro ni impamo"
  38,65,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Njye nta kindi ndi cyo usibye kuba ndi umuburizi, kandi nta yindi mana ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri itari Allah; Umwe rukumbi, Umunyembaraga w’ikirenga"
  38,66,"Nyagasani w’ibirere n’isi ndetse n’ibiri hagati yabyo, Umunyembaraga zihebuje,Umunyembabazi uhebuje"
  38,67,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Iyi (Qur’an) ni inkuru ihambaye"
  38,68,Ariko mwayiteye umugongo
  38,69,Nta bumenyi nari mfite ku mpaka zagibwaga n’abamalayika bo mu ijuru (ku iremwa rya Adamu)
  38,70,Usibye ko nabihishuriwe kuko ndi umuburizi ugaragara
  38,71,"(Ibuka) ubwo Nyagasani wawe yabwiraga abamalayika ati \"Mu by’ukuri, ngiye kurema umuntu mu ibumba"
  38,72,"Nimara kumutunganya nkanamuhuhamo roho, mumwikubite imbere mwubamye"
  38,73,Nuko abamalayika bose barubama
  38,74,Usibye Ibilisi (Shitani) wagize ubwibone maze akaba mu bahakanye
  38,75,"(Nuko Allah akavuga ati) \"Yewe Ibilisi! Ni iki cyakubujije kubamira uwo naremye n’amaboko yanjye yombi? Ese wagize ubwibone cyangwa wabaye mu bishyize hejuru"
  38,76,"(Ibilisi) iravuga iti \"Njye ndi mwiza kumurusha kuko wandemye mu muriro, we ukamurema mu ibumba"
  38,77,"Allah aravuga ati \"Ngaho sohoka aha ( mu ijuru), kuko ubaye ikivume"
  38,78,Kandi rwose umuvumo wanjye uzagukurikirana kuzageza ku munsi w’ibihembo
  38,79,"(Ibilisi) iravuga iti \"Nyagasani wanjye! Mpa kuramba kuzageza ku munsi (abapfuye) bazazurirwaho"
  38,80,"(Allah) aravuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, ubaye mu bazaramba"
  38,81,Kugeza ku munsi w’igihe kizwi
  38,82,"(Ibilisi) iravuga iti \"Ndahiye ku bw’icyubahiro cyawe, ko rwose nzabayobya bose"
  38,83,Uretse abagaragu bawe b’indobanure muri bo
  38,84,"(Allah) avuga arahira ati \"Ni ukuri, kandi ibyo mvuga ni ukuri"
  38,85,Ko wowe na bamwe mu bazagukurikira nzabuzurisha umuriro wa Jahanamu
  38,86,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ntabwo (kubagezaho ubutumwa) mbibasabira igihembo na kimwe, ndetse nta n’ubwo ndi mu bishushanya (bakora ibyo batategetswe)"
  38,87,Iyi (Qur’an) nta kindi iri cyo usibye kuba ari urwibutso ku biremwa byose
  38,88,"Kandi rwose muzamenya inkuru yayo bidatinze\" Yahishuriwe i Maka, ig"
  39,1,"Ihishurwa ry’iki gitabo (Qur’an) rituruka kwa Allah, Umunyembaraga uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  39,2,"Mu by’ukuri, (yewe Muhamadi) twaguhishuriye igitabo mu kuri. Bityo, jya usenga Allah umwibombaritseho"
  39,3,"Mumenye ko Allah ari we nyir’idini ritunganye. Naho babandi bishyiriyeho ibigirwamana mu cyimbo cye, (baravuga bati) \"Nta yindi mpamvu ituma tubisenga itari ukugira ngo bitwegereze Allah\". Mu by’ukuri, Allah azabakiranura ku byo batavugagaho rumwe. Rwose Allah ntayobora umunyabinyoma, umuhakanyi wa cyane"
  39,4,"Iyo Allah aza gukenera kugira umwana, yari gutoranya uwo ashaka mu byo yaremye. Ubutagatifu ni ubwe! Ni we Allah, Umwe rukumbi, Umunyembaraga z’ikirenga"
  39,5,"Yaremye ibirere n’isi mu kuri. Yorosa ijoro ku manywa akanorosa amanywa ku ijoro. Anacisha bugufi izuba n’ukwezi; buri kimwe kizenguruka (mu mbibi zacyo) ku gihe cyagenwe. Mumenye ko we (Allah) ari Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Umunyembabazi uhebuje"
  39,6,"Yabaremye abakomoye ku muntu umwe (Adamu), nuko amuremera umugore we (Hawa) amumukomoyemo. Yabaremeye amatungo umunani (ingabo n’ingore mu ngamiya, inka, intama ndetse n’ihene). Abaremera muri nyababyeyi za ba nyoko, mu byiciro bikurikirana, mu myijima itatu (mu nda, muri nyababyeyi no mu ngobyi). Uwo ni we Allah Nyagasani wanyu, Nyir’ubwami bwose. Nta yindi mana ikwiriye gusengwa by’ukuri itari we. Ese ni gute mureka kugaragira (Allah wenyine)"
  39,7,"(Yemwe bantu) nimuramuka muhakanye, mu by’ukuri, Allah arihagije (ntacyo abakeneyeho), ndetse ntiyishimira ubuhakanyi ku bagaragu be. Ariko iyo mushimiye (mukanemera), arabyishimira. Kandi ntawe uzikorera umutwaro w’undi. Hanyuma igarukiro ryanyu rizaba kwa Nyagasani wanyu, maze ababwire ibyo mwakoraga. Mu by’ukuri, we ni Umumenyi uhebuje w’ibiri mu bituza (by’abantu)"
  39,8,"N’iyo umuntu agezweho n’amakuba, asaba Nyagasani we amwicuzaho. Nyamara (Allah) yamuha ku ngabire ze, akibagirwa icyatumaga asaba mbere, maze agashyiraho ibigirwamana bibangikanye na Allah, kugira ngo ayobye (abantu) kugana inzira ye. Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Inezeze gake mu buhakanyi bwawe! Mu by’ukuri, uri mubazajya mu muriro"
  39,9,"Ese wawundi usenga (Allah) mu bihe by’ijoro, yubama, anahagarara (kubera) gutinya imperuka, aniringira impuhwe za Nyagasani we (ni kimwe na wa wundi uhakana Allah?) Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ese abafite ubumenyi bahwanye n’abatabufite? Mu by’ukuri, abanyabwenge ni bo babizirikana"
  39,10,"Vuga uti \"Yemwe bagaragu banjye bemeye! Nimutinye Nyagasani wanyu; babandi bakoze neza kuri iyi si bazagororerwa ibyiza (Ijuru). Kandi isi ya Allah ni ngari (niba aho muri bitaborohera gusenga Allah, nimwimukire ahandi). Mu by’ukuri, abihangana bazagororerwa ibihembo byabo byuzuye, nta kubara"
  39,11,"Vuga uti \"Mu by’ukuri, njye nategetswe kugaragira Allah (wenyine) nkora ibikorwa byiza kubera we"
  39,12,Kandi nategetswe kuba uwa mbere mu bicisha bugufi (Abayislamu)
  39,13,"Vuga uti \"Mu by’ukuri, mfite ubwoba bw’ibihano by’umunsi uhambaye, igihe naba nigometse kuri Nyagasani wanjye"
  39,14,"Vuga uti \"Ngaragira Allah wenyine nkora ibikorwa byiza kubera we"
  39,15,"Ngaho nimugaragire ibyo mushaka bitari we.Vuga uti \"Mu by’ukuri, abanyagihombo ku munsi w’imperuka ni babandi bazaba baroretse roho zabo ndetse n’iz’imiryango yabo\". Rwose icyo kizaba ari cyo gihombo kigaragara"
  39,16,"Bazaba batwikiriwe n’igicu cy’umuriro ndetse no munsi yabo hari ikindi. Ibyo ni byo Allah atinyisha abagaragu be. Bityo bagaragu banjye, nimuntinye"
  39,17,"Naho babandi bitandukanyije no gusenga ibigirwamana bakagarukira Allah (bamwicuzaho), bateganyirijwe inkuru nziza. Bityo, geza inkuru nziza ku bagaragu banjye"
  39,18,Babandi batega amatwi amagambo (menshi avugwa) maze bagakurikira ameza muri yo. Abo ni bo Allah yayoboye kandi ni bo banyabwenge
  39,19,Nonese wawundi uzahamwa n’ijambo ry’ibihano (washobora kumuyobora)? Ese washobora kurokora uri mu muriro
  39,20,"Ariko babandi batinya Nyagasani wabo, bazagororerwa amazu yubatse agerekeranye; imigezi itemba imbere yayo. (Iri) ni isezerano rya Allah, kandi Allah ntajya yica isezerano"
  39,21,"Ese ntujya ubona ko Allah yamanuye amazi mu kirere maze akayinjiza mu butaka, hanyuma akaba amasoko nuko akayameresha ibihingwa by’amabara atandukanye, hanyuma bikuma ukabona bibaye umuhondo; nuko (byamara kumagana) akabihindura utuvungukira? Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo hari urwibutso ku banyabwenge"
  39,22,"Ese uwo Allah yaguriye igituza (akayoboka) Isilamu, akanaba mu rumuri ruturutse kwa Nyagasani we (yaba kimwe n’ufite umutima winangiye)? Bityo, ibihano bikomeye bizaba ku bafite imitima inangiye, itibuka Allah. Abo bari mu buyobe bugaragara"
  39,23,"Allah yahishuye inkuru nziza kurusha izindi; ari cyo gitabo (Qur’an) gifite imirongo yuzuzanya kandi yisubiramo (itarambirana), ituma imibiri y’abatinya Nyagasani wabo ikangarana (iyo bayumvise isomwa), hanyuma imibiri n’imitima byabo bikoroha (bikabasha) gusingiza Allah. Uwo ni wo muyoboro wa Allah ayoboresha uwo ashatse; kandi uwo Allah yarekeye mu buyobe ntiyagira uwamuyobora"
  39,24,"Ese uzaba ahungisha uburanga bwe ibihano bibi byo ku munsi w’imperuka (yaba kimwe n’uzinjira mu ijuru mu buryo bworoshye)? Icyo gihe inkozi z’ibibi zizabwirwa ziti \"Ngaho nimusogongere ibyo mwakoraga"
  39,25,Ababayeho mbere yabo barahakanye maze bagerwaho n’ibihano mu buryo batazi
  39,26,"Nuko Allah abasogongeza ugusuzugurika mu buzima bwo ku isi, kandi ibihano byo ku mperuka ni byo biruta ibindi; iyaba bari babizi"
  39,27,Kandi rwose twahaye abantu ingero z’ubwoko bwose muri iyi Qur’an kugira ngo bibuke
  39,28,"Qur’an yahishuwe mu rurimi rw’Icyarabu izira amakemwa, kugira ngo batinye (Allah)"
  39,29,"Allah yatanze urugero rw’umuntu (umugaragu) uhatswe na ba shebuja benshi batavuga rumwe, n’umuntu uhatswe na shebuja umwe. Ese abo bombi wabagereranya? Ishimwe n’ikuzo byuzuye ni ibya Allah, ariko abenshi muri bo ntibabizi"
  39,30,"Mu by’ukuri, wowe (Muhamadi) uzapfa kandi na bo bazapfa"
  39,31,Hanyuma mwese ku munsi w’imperuka muzahagarare imbere ya Nyagasani wanyu mujya impaka
  39,32,"Ni nde nkozi y’ibibi ya cyane kurusha uhimbira Allah ikinyoma, akanahakana ukuri igihe kumugezeho? Ese mu muriro wa Jahanamu si ho buturo bw’abahakanyi"
  39,33,Naho uwazanye ukuri (Qur’an) ndetse n’abakwemeye; abo ni bo batinyamana
  39,34,Bazabona ibyo bazifuza byose kwa Nyagasani wabo. Ibyo ni byo bihembo by’abakora ibyiza
  39,35,(Ibyo) ni ukugira ngo Allah abababarire ibibi bakoze kandi anabahembere ibyiza bakoraga
  39,36,Ese Allah ntahagije (kuba umurinzi w’) umugaragu we? Nyamara bagukangisha (ibyo basenga) bitari we! Kandi uwo Allah yarekeye mu buyobe ntiyagira uwamuyobora
  39,37,"Kandi uwo Allah yashoboje kuyoboka ntawamuyobya. Ese Allah si Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Nyir’uguhora"
  39,38,"N’iyo ubabajije uti \"Ni nde waremye ibirere n’isi\"? Rwose baravuga bati \"Ni Allah\". Vuga uti \"Ngaho nimumbwire! Ese ibyo musenga bitari Allah, Allah aramutse ashatse ko icyago kimbaho byagikuraho? Cyangwa agashaka ko impuhwe zingeraho, byakumira impuhwe ze\"? Vuga uti \" Allah arampagije kandi abiringira bajye ari we biringira"
  39,39,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Yemwe bantu banjye! Nimukore uko mubishaka, nanjye ndakora (nk’uko Allah yantegetse). Hanyuma muzamenya"
  39,40,"Uzagerwaho n’ibihano bimusuzuguza (hano ku isi), ndetse akazanagerwaho n’ibihano bihoraho"
  39,41,"Rwose twaguhishuriye igitabo mu kuri kigenewe abantu bose. Bityo, uyobotse aba yigiriye neza ndetse n’uyobye aba yihemukiye. Kandi wowe ntabwo uri umuhagararizi wabo"
  39,42,"Allah ni we utwara roho z’abantu iyo igihe cyazo cyo gupfa kigeze, ndetse (ni nawe utwara) iz’abasinziriye igihe cyazo cyo gupfa kitaragera. Nuko akagumana roho z’abo yageneye (gupfa), maze izindi akazohereza (mu mibiri yazo, zikabaho) kugeza igihe cyagenwe. Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo harimo ibimenyetso ku bantu batekereza"
  39,43,"Ese (ababangikanyamana) bishyiriyeho abavugizi batari Allah? Vuga uti \"Nonese n’iyo baba ntacyo batunze cyangwa bazi (mukomeza kubiringira)"
  39,44,"Vuga uti \"Ubuvugizi bwose ni ubwa Allah. Ni we Nyir’ubwami bw’ibirere n’isi. Kandi iwe ni ho muzagarurwa"
  39,45,"Kandi iyo havuzwe Allah wenyine, imitima y’abatemera imperuka irabyinubira, nyamara havugwa ibitari we (Allah), bakanezerwa"
  39,46,"Vuga uti \"Nyagasani wanjye! Muremyi w’ibirere n’isi! Umumenyi w’ibitagaragara n’ibigaragara! Ni wowe uzakiranura abagaragu bawe ku byo batavugagaho rumwe"
  39,47,"Kandi iyo abahakanyi baza kuba bafite ibiri mu isi byose ndetse n’ibindi nka byo, bari kubitangaho inshungu kugira ngo bibarinde ibihano bibi byo ku munsi w’imperuka. Kandi bazagaragarirwa n’ibyo batakekaga (ibihano) biturutse kwa Allah"
  39,48,"Ndetse bazanagaragarizwa ibibi bakoze, kandi bazazengurukwa n’ibyo bajyaga bannyega"
  39,49,"N’iyo umuntu agezweho n’amakuba, aradusaba hanyuma (ya makuba) twayahinduramo ingabire ziduturutseho, akavuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, ibi nabihawe kubera ubumenyi bwanjye (ku bw’ibyo sinkeneye gushimira Allah). (Si ko bimeze,) ahubwo ni ibigeragezo, uretse ko abenshi muri bo batabizi"
  39,50,"Rwose abababanjirije bavuze nk’ibi, ariko ibyo bakoraga nta cyo byabamariye"
  39,51,"Nuko bagerwaho n’ingaruka z’ibyo bakoze. Kandi na babandi bakoze ibibi muri bo bazagerwaho n’ingaruka z’ibibi bakoze, ndetse ntibananiye (Allah kuba yabahana bakiri ku isi)"
  39,52,"Ese ntibazi ko Allah yongerera amafunguro uwo ashatse akanayagabanyiriza (uwo ashatse)? Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo hari inyigisho ku bantu bemera"
  39,53,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Yemwe bagaragu banjye bihemukiye! Ntimwihebe kuko impuhwe za Allah zikiriho. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ababarira ibyaha byose. Kandi ni Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  39,54,"Kandi nimwicuze kwa Nyagasani wanyu munamwicisheho bugufi mbere y’uko mugerwaho n’ibihano, hanyuma ntimutabarwe"
  39,55,"Munakurikire ibyiza mwahishuriwe (Qor’an) biturutse kwa Nyagasani wanyu, mbere y’uko mugerwaho n’ibihano bibatunguye mutabizi"
  39,56,"(Ibyo ni) ukugira ngo hatazagira uvuga ati \"Mbega akaga ngizekubera kudohoka ku mategeko ya Allah, kandi rwose nari umwe mu bayakerensaga"
  39,57,"Cyangwa akavuga ati \"Rwose iyo Allah aza kunyobora, nari kuba mu batinyamana"
  39,58,"Cyangwa se igihe azaba abonye ibihano akavuga ati \"Rwose iyaba nari (mbonye amahirwe yo kugaruka ku isi), nari kuzaba mu bakora ibyiza"
  39,59,"(Azasubizwa ati) \"Niko biri! Rwose wagezweho n’ibimenyetso byanjye maze urabihakana, uribona ndetse uba umwe mu bahakanyi"
  39,60,"Ndetse no ku munsi w’imperuka, uzabona uburanga bwa babandi bahimbiye Allah (ibinyoma) bwijimye. Ese muri Jahanamu si ho buturo bw’abibone"
  39,61,Kandi Allah azarokora babandi batinye Nyagasani wabo abaha ibyicaro byabo byiza (mu Ijuru). Ntibazigera bagerwaho n’ikibi (icyo ari cyo cyose) ndetse ntibazagira n’agahinda
  39,62,"Allah ni Umuremyi wa buri kintu, kandi ni na we muhagararizi wa buri kintu"
  39,63,"Ni we nyir’imfunguzo z’ibiri mu birere no mu isi. Naho babandi bahakanye ibimenyetso bya Allah, ni bo bazaba abanyagihombo"
  39,64,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ese ibitari Allah ni byo muntegeka kugaragira, yemwe mwa njiji mwe"
  39,65,"Kandi rwose warahishuriwe (wowe Muhamadi) nk’uko (intumwa) zakubanjirije (zahishuriwe) ko nuramuka ubangikanyije Allah, ibikorwa byawe byose bizaba impfabusa, kandi nta kabuza uzaba mu banyagihombo"
  39,66,"Ahubwo Allah (wenyine) ube ari we usenga, kandi ube umwe mu bashimira"
  39,67,"Kandi (ababangikanyamana) ntabwo bahaye Allah icyubahiro kimukwiye. No ku munsi w’imperuka ibiri mu isi byose bizaba biri mu kuboko kwe, ndetse n’ibirere bizazingazingirwa mu kuboko kwe kw’iburyo. Ubutagatifu ni ubwe kandi ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamubangikanya (nabyo)"
  39,68,"Nuko ubwo impanda izavuzwa, abari mu birere no mu isi bazagwa igihumure (bapfe), uretse uwo Allah azashaka. Hanyuma yongere ivuzwe bwa kabiri, maze bahaguruke (bazuke bose) bategereje (uko Allah ari bubagenze)"
  39,69,"Kandi isi izamurikirwa n’urumuri rwa Nyagasani wayo, nuko buri wese ahabwe igitabo (cy’ibikorwa bye), hanyuma abahanuzi n’abahamya bazanwe, maze (abantu) bacirwe urubanza mu kuri, badahugujwe"
  39,70,"Na buri wese azahemberwa ibyo yakoze, kandi (Allah) ni we uzi bihebuje ibyo bakoraga"
  39,71,"Abahakanyi bazashorerwa bajyanwa muri Jahanamu mu dutsiko, kugeza ubwo bazayigeraho maze imiryango yayo igafunguka, nuko abarinzi bayo bavuge bati \"Ese ntimwagezweho n’intumwa zibaturutsemo, zibasomera amagambo (Ayat) ya Nyagasani wanyu, ndetse zinababurira kuzahura n’uyu munsi wanyu?\"Bazavuga bati \"Yego! Ahubwo ijambo ry’ibihano ryabaye impamo ku bahakanyi (ari bo twe)"
  39,72,"Nuko babwirwe bati \"Nimwinjire mu miryango ya Jahanamu, muzabamo ubuziraherezo. Kandi ni bwo buturo bubi bw’abibone"
  39,73,"Naho babandi batinye Nyagasani wabo, bazayoborwa mu ijuru bari mu matsinda kugeza ubwo bazarigeraho maze imiryango yaryo ifunguke, nuko abarinzi baryo bavuge bati \"Amahoro nabe kuri mwe! Mwakoze neza, ngaho nimuryinjiremo (muribemo) ubuziraherezo"
  39,74,"Nabo bavuge bati \"Ishimwe n’ikuzo ni ibya Allah, we wubahirije isezerano rye akanaduha kuzungura ubutaka bw’Ijuru tukaba dutuye aho dushaka. Ku bw’ibyo, ibihembo byiza ni iby’abakora neza"
  39,75,"Uzabona kandi abamalayika bakikije intebe y’ubwami (ya Allah), basingiza ikuzo n’ishimwe bya Nyagasani wabo. Kandi (ibiremwa byose) bizakiranurwa mu kuri. Nuko havugwe ngo \"Ishimwe n’ikuzo byuzuye ni ibya Allah, Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose"
  40,1,Haa Miimu
  40,2,"Ihishurwa ry’igitabo (Qur’an) rituruka kuri Allah, Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  40,3,"Ubabarira ibyaha, Uwakira ukwicuza, Nyir’ibihano bikaze, Nyir’ingabire. Nta yindi mana ibaho itari we, kandi iwe ni ho garukiro"
  40,4,"Nta bajya impaka ku bimenyetso bya Allah, usibye babandi bahakanye. Bityo, ntugashukwe no kwidegembya kwabo ku isi"
  40,5,"Mbere yabo (Abakurayishi), n’abantu ba Nuhu ndetse n’udutsiko twaje nyuma yabo barahakanye. Kandi buri muryango w’abantu washatse kwica intumwa yawutumweho, ndetse bajya impaka zishingiye ku kinyoma bagamije kuburizamo ukuri, maze ndabafata (ndabahana). Mbega uko ibihano byanjye byari bimeze"
  40,6,"Uko ni ko ijambo rya Nyagasani wawe (ry’ibihano) ryabaye impamo kuri babandi bahakanye, ko rwose ari abantu bo mu muriro"
  40,7,"Babandi (abamalayika) bateruye intebe y’ubwami (Arshi) n’abayikikije, basingiza ikuzo rya Nyagasani wabo bakanamwemera, bakanasabira imbabazi ba bandi bemera (bagira bati) \"Nyagasani wacu! Impuhwe n’ubumenyi byawe byageze kuri buri kintu. None babarira ibyaha babandi bakwicujijeho, bakanakurikira inzira yawe ndetse unabarinde ibihano byo mu muriro"
  40,8,"Nyagasani wacu! Unabinjize mu ijuru rihoraho wabasezeranyije, ndetse unahe n’abari intungane mu bakurambere babo, mu bagore babo no mu rubyaro rwabo. Mu by’ukuri, ni wowe Munyembaraga Ushishoza uhebuje\". zihebuje"
  40,9,"Kandi unabarinde ibibi, kuko uwo uzarinda ibibi kuri uwo munsi rwose uzaba umugiriye impuhwe. Kandi iyo niyo ntsinzi ihambaye"
  40,10,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bahakanye (ubwo bazaba binjizwa mu muriro) bazabwirwa bati \"Rwose uburakari bwa Allah(abafitiye) burakomeye cyane kuruta ubwo mufitanye hagati yanyu (muri mu muriro), kubera ko mwajyaga muhamagarirwa kwemera ariko mugahakana"
  40,11,"Bazavuga bati \"Nyagasani wacu! Watwambuye ubuzima ubugira kabiri (mbere y’ivuka ryacu n’igihe twavaga ku isi), unaduha ubuzima ubugira kabiri (igihe twavukaga n’igihe watuzuraga), none ubu twemeye ibyaha byacu. Ese haba hari inzira yo gusohoka (muri uyu muriro tukagaruka ku isi gukora ibikorwa byiza)"
  40,12,"Ibyo ni ukubera ko iyo mwahamagarirwaga gusenga Allah wenyine, mwarahakanaga. Nyamara yabangikanywa (n’ibindi) mukaba ari bwo mwemera. Bityo, ubucamanza ni ubwa Allah, Uwikirenga, Usumbabyose"
  40,13,"(Allah) ni we ubereka ibimenyetso bye, akanabamanurira mu kirere (imvura ituma mubona) amafunguro, nyamara ntawuzirikana (ibyo bimenyetso) usibye ugarukira (Allah)"
  40,14,"Bityo, nimwambaze Allah wenyine mumwegurira ibikorwa byanyu, kabone n’iyo byababaza abahakanyi"
  40,15,"(Ni we) ufite urwego rusumba izindi, nyir’intebe y’ubwami. Ku bw’itegeko rye, yohereza Roho (Malayika Jibril) k’uwo ashatse mu bagaragu be, kugira ngo aburire (abantu) umunsi bazahurira (hamwe)"
  40,16,"Umunsi bose bazagaragara, nta na kimwe mu byabo kizihisha Allah. (Allah azavuga ati) \"Uyu munsi ubwami ni ubwa nde?\" (Allah azisubiza agira ati) \"Ni ubwa Allah, Umwe rukumbi, Umunyembaraga z’ikirenga"
  40,17,"Uyu munsi buri wese arahemberwa ibyo yakoze. Uyu munsi nta mahugu (agirirwa uwo ari we wese). Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni ubanguka mu ibarura"
  40,18,"Unababurire umunsi wegereje, ubwo imitima izaba ibageze mu ngoto bafite ubwoba. Inkozi z’ibibi nta nshuti zizagira ndetse (zizagira) uzumvwa. nta n’umuvugizi"
  40,19,(Allah) azi neza amaso yuzuye uburyarya ndetse n’ibyo imitima ihishe
  40,20,"Kandi Allah aca imanza mu kuri, naho ibyo basenga bitari we, nta bubasha bifite bwo guca urubanza na rumwe. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Uwumva cyane, Ubona bihebuje"
  40,21,"Ese ntibatambagira isi ngo barebe uko iherezo ry’abababanjirije ryagenze? Bari bafite imbaraga n’ibikorwa bihambaye ku isi kubarusha, nuko Allah abahanira ibyaha byabo. Kandi ntibigeze bagira ubarinda (ibihano bya) Allah"
  40,22,"Ibyo ni ukubera ko intumwa zabo zabageragaho zibazaniye ibitangaza bigaragara, maze bagahakana. Nuko Allah arabahana. Mu by’ukuri, ni Umunyembaraga, Nyir’ibihano bikaze"
  40,23,Kandi rwose twohereje Musa tumuhaye ibimenyetso byacu n’ubutware bigaragara
  40,24,"(Tumwohereza) kwa Farawo, Hamana na Qaruna, nuko baravuga bati \"(Uyu) ni umurozi w’umubeshyi"
  40,25,"Maze ubwo (Musa) yabageragaho abazaniye ukuri kuduturutseho, baravuze bati \"Nimwice abahungu mu bana b’abamwemeye, mureke abakobwa. Ariko imigambi y’abahakanyi iganisha mu buyobe"
  40,26,"Nuko Farawo aravuga ati \"Nimundeke nice Musa, maze ahamagare Nyagasani we (amutabare). Mu by’ukuri, ndatinya ko yahindura idini ryanyu cyangwa agakwirakwiza ubwononnyi mu gihugu (Misiri)"
  40,27,"Musa aravuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, nikinze kuri Nyagasani wanjye ari na we Nyagasani wanyu, ngo andinde buri wese wibona, utemera umunsi w’ibarura"
  40,28,"Maze umwemera wo mu bantu ba Farawo, wahishaga ukwemera kwe, aravuga ati \"Ese murica umuntu mumuhora ko avuga ati Nyagasani wanjye ni Allah?’ Kandi abazaniye ibimenyetso bigaragara biturutse kwa Nyagasani wanyu? Niba ari umubeshyi, ikinyoma cye kizamugaruka, kandi niba ari umunyakuri, bimwe mu byo abasezeranya bizababaho. Rwose Allah ntayobora urengera (amategeko ye), umunyakinyoma"
  40,29,"(Akomeza agira ati) \"Yemwe bantu banjye, uyu munsi mufite ubwami, mwaratsinze ku isi, none ni nde wadutabara biramutse ibihano bya bitugezeho?\" Allah Farawo aravuga ati \"Nta gitekerezo nabaha uretse icyo mbona (ko cyabagirira akamaro), ndetse nta n’ubwo mbayobora uretse kubaganisha mu nzira itunganye"
  40,30,"Nuko wawundi wemeye aravuga ati \"Yemwe bantu banjye! Mu by’ukuri, ndatinya ko mwazagerwaho n’ibihano nk’ibyabaye ku munsi w’udutsiko"
  40,31,"(Ibyo bihano) ni nk’ibyabaye ku bantu ba Nuhu, aba Adi, aba Thamudu n’ababayeho nyuma yabo. Kandi Allah ntabwo agamije kurenganya abagaragu (be)"
  40,32,"Yemwe bantu banjye! Mu by’ukuri, ndatinya ko mwazagerwaho (n’ibihano) ku munsi wo guhamagarana (hagati y’abantu bo mu ijuru n’abo mu muriro)"
  40,33,"Umunsi (muzabona umuriro) mugahindukira muhunga, ntimuzabona ubarinda (ibihano bya) Allah\". Kandi uwo Allah yarekeye mu buyobe ntiyagira uwamuyobora"
  40,34,"Kandi rwose Yusuf yari yarabagezeho na mbere afite ibimenyetso bigaragara, ariko mwagumye mu gushidikanya ku byo abazaniye. Nuko ubwo yaramaze gupfa, muravuga muti \" Allah ntazigera yohereza indi ntumwa nyuma ye. Uko ni ko Allah arekera mu buyobe wawundi urengera, ushidikanya"
  40,35,"Babandi bajya impaka ku magambo ya Allah nta gihamya babifitiye, (ibyo) birakaza Allah bikomeye ndetse n’abemera. Uko ni ko Allah adanangira umutima wa wawundi w’umwibone, icyigomeke"
  40,36,"Farawo aravuga ati \"Yewe Hamana! Nyubakira umunara kugira ngo mbashe kugera mu mayira"
  40,37,"Amayira yo mu birere, no kugira ngo nshobore kubona Imana ya Musa; ariko ndakeka ko (Musa) ari umubeshyi\". Uko ni ko Farawo yakundishijwe ibikorwa bye bibi maze akumirwa mu nzira y’ukuri. Kandi ubugambanyi bwa Farawo ntacyo bwamumariye uretse ko bwatumye arimbuka"
  40,38,"Naho wawundi wemeye (wo mu bantu ba Farawo) aravuga ati \"Yemwe bantu banjye! Nimunkurikire mbayobore mu nzira itunganye"
  40,39,"Yemwe bantu banjye! Mu by’ukuri, ubu buzima bw’isi ni umunezero w’igihe gito, kandi rwose (ubuzima bw’) imperuka ni bwo buturo buzahoraho"
  40,40,"Uzakora igikorwa kibi azahembwa ikingana nacyo, na ho uzakora igikorwa cyiza, yaba umugabo cyangwa umugore akaba ari n’umwemera; abo nibo bazinjira mu ijuru, bahabwe amafunguro nta kugera"
  40,41,"Yemwe bantu banjye! Kuki mbahamagarira kurokoka, mwe mukampamagarira kugana umuriro"
  40,42,"Murampamagarira guhakana Allah ngo mubangikanye n’ibyo ntafitiye ubumenyi? Nyamara njye ndabahamagarira kugana (Allah) Nyir’imbaraga zihebuje, Ubabarira ibyaha"
  40,43,"Nta kabuza ko ibyo mumpamagarira ntacyo byamarira mu byo nabisaba, haba ku isi cyangwa ku mperuka, kandi igarukiro ryacu ni kwa Allah. Kandi abarengera imbago (za Allah) ni bo bantu bo mu muriro"
  40,44,"Kandi muzibuka ibyo mbabwira! Nanjye ibyanjye mbyeguriye Allah! Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Ubona abagaragu be mu buryo buhebuje"
  40,45,"Nuko Allah amurinda imigambi mibisha yabo bari bagambiriye, maze ibihano bibi bigera ku bantu ba Farawo"
  40,46,"Umuriro bawushyirwamo mu gitondo na nimunsi (aho bari mu mva zabo), n’igihe umunsi w’imperuka wageze (abamalayika bazabwirwa bati): \"Nimwinjize abantu ba Farawo mu bihano (umuriro) bibabaza cyane"
  40,47,"Kandi zirikana ubwo bazatongana bari mu muriro baterana amagambo, maze abanyantegenke babwire babandi bibonaga (ku isi) bati \"Mu by’ukuri, ni mwe twakurikiraga. Ese none hari icyo mwatumarira, mu kutugabanyiriza kuri ibi bihano by’umuriro"
  40,48,"Babandi bibonaga (ku isi) bazavuga bati \"Rwose twese tuwurimo! Mu by’ukuri, Allah yamaze gukiranura abagaragu be"
  40,49,"Nuko abari mu muriro bazabwire abarinzi ba Jahanamu bati \"Nimudusabire Nyagasani wanyu atugabanyirize ibihano kabone n’ubwo byaba umunsi umwe"
  40,50,"(Bazababwira bati \"Ese intumwa zanyu ntizabageragaho zibazaniye ibimenyetso bigaragara?\" Bavuge bati \"Nibyo b’umuriro) (zatugezeho)!\" bavuge bati (Abarinzi \"Ngaho nimusabe ariko ugusaba kw’abahakanyi ntacyo kumara uretse igihombo)"
  40,51,"Mu by’ukuri, dutabara intumwa zacu na babandi bemeye (Intumwa bakazikurikira) bakiri mu buzima bw’isi, no ku munsi abahamya bazahagarara (babashinja ibyo bakoze)"
  40,52,"Umunsi urwitwazo rw’inkozi z’ibibi rutazagira icyo ruzimarira, ndetse bazagira umuvumo n’ubuturo bubi"
  40,53,"Kandi rwose twahaye Musa umuyoboro (Tawurati), tunaha bene Isiraheli kuba abazungura b’icyo gitabo"
  40,54,Ngo kibe umuyoboro n’urwibutso ku bafite ubwenge
  40,55,"Bityo (yewe Muhamadi) ihangane! Mu by’ukuri, isezerano rya Allah ni ukuri. Kandi usabe imbabazi z’ibyaha byawe, ndetse unasingize ikuzo rya Nyagasani wawe buri uko bwije na buri uko bucyeye"
  40,56,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bajya impaka ku magambo ya Allah nta gihamya yabagezeho, rwose nta kindi kiri mu mitima yabo usibye ubwibone (bwo gushaka gusumba intumwa), kandi ntibazabigeraho. Bityo, jya wikinga kuri Allah (akurinde ibibi byabo). Mu by’ukuri, ni we Uwumva cyane, Ubona bihebuje"
  40,57,Rwose iremwa ry’ibirere n’isi ni ryo rikomeye kuruta iremwa ry’abantu (no kubazura); nyamara abenshi mu bantu ntibabizi
  40,58,"Kandi utabona ntabwo ari kimwe n’ubona, ndetse na babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza si kimwe n’abakora ibibi. Ariko ibyo mwibuka ni bike"
  40,59,"Mu by’ukuri, imperuka izaza nta kuyishidikanyaho, ariko abenshi mu bantu ntibabyemera"
  40,60,"Kandi Nyagasani wanyu yaravuze ati \"Nimunsabe, ndabasubiza. Mu by’ukuri, babandi bibona bakanga kunsenga (kunsaba), bazinjira mu muriro basuzuguritse"
  40,61,"Allah ni we wabashyiriyeho ijoro kugira ngo muriruhukemo ndetse anabashyiriraho amanywa kugira ngo mubashe kubona (bityo mushake ibibabeshaho). Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni nyir’ingabire ku bantu; nyamara abenshi mu bantu ntibashima"
  40,62,"Uwo ni Allah Nyagasani wanyu, Umuremyi wa buri kintu, nta yindi mana ibaho itari we. Ese ni gute mureka ukuri (mugasenga ibitari Allah)"
  40,63,Uko ni ko abahakanaga ibimenyetso bya Allah bateshwaga ukuri
  40,64,"Allah yabashyiriyeho isi nk’ahantu ho gutura kandi hatekanye, (anabaremera) ikirere kiyitwikiriye, nuko abaha amashusho maze arayatunganya, ndetse abaha n’amafunguro meza. Uwo ni we Allah, Nyagasani wanyu. Bityo, ubutagatifu ni ubwa Allah, Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose"
  40,65,"Ni we Uhoraho, nta yindi mana ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri uretse we. Bityo, nimumusabe mumwibombaritseho. Ishimwe n’ikuzo byuzuye ni ibya Allah, Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose"
  40,66,"Vuga uti \"Mu by’ukuri, nabujijwe gusenga ibyo musenga bitari Allah, ubwo nagerwagaho n’ibimenyetso bigaragara biturutse kwa Nyagasani wanjye. Kandi nategetswe kwicisha bugufi imbere ya Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose"
  40,67,"Ni we wabaremye abakomoye mu gitaka, hanyuma mu ntanga, hanyuma mu rusoro rw’amaraso, hanyuma abasohora muri (nyababyeyi) muri impinja, hanyuma arabakuza muba ibikwerere, hanyuma muba abasaza. No muri mwe harimo abapfa mbere, (Allah abikora gutyo) kugira ngo (mubeho kugeza) ku gihe cyagenwe, ngo wenda mwagira ubwenge"
  40,68,"Ni we utanga ubuzima akanatanga n’urupfu. Kandi iyo ategetse ko ikintu (kiba), mu by’ukuri, arakibwira ngo \"Ba!\" maze kikaba"
  40,69,Ese ntubona babandi bajya impaka ku magambo ya Allah? Ni gute bareka ukuri (bakajya mu buyobe)
  40,70,"Babandi bahinyuye igitabo (Qur’an) ndetse n’ibindi (bitabo) twoherereje intumwa zacu, vuba aha bazamenya (ko ibyo barimo atari ukuri)"
  40,71,Ubwo bazazirikwa imigozi y’ibyuma n’iminyururu mu majosi bakururwa
  40,72,"(Bagaragurwa) mu mazi yatuye, hanyuma batwikirwe mu muriro"
  40,73,"Maze babwirwe bati \"Bya (bigirwamana) biri hehe mwajyaga musenga"
  40,74,"Muretse Allah?\" Bavuge bati \"Twabibuze! Ahubwo na mbere nta n’ibyo twasengaga\". Uko ni ko Allah arekera abahakanyi mu buyobe"
  40,75,"Ibyo (bihano mubihawe) kubera ko ku isi mwajyaga mwishimira (ibangikanyamana) bitari mu kuri, ndetse no kubera ko mwajyaga mwishimira cyane (ibibi mwakoraga)"
  40,76,"Ngaho nimwinjire mu miryango y’umuriro wa Jahanamu, muzabamo ubuziraherezo. Kandi ni bwo buturo bubi bw’abibone"
  40,77,"Bityo, jya wihangana (yewe Muhamadi), mu by’ukuri, isezerano rya Allah ni ukuri. Kandi n’iyo twakwereka bimwe mu byo tubasezeranya (ukiri ku isi), cyangwa tukakuzuriza igihe cyawe (ugapfa), uko byagenda kose iwacu ni ho bazagarurwa"
  40,78,"Kandi rwose twohereje intumwa (nyinshi) mbere yawe; muri zo hari izo twakubariye inkuru zazo, ndetse hari n’izo tutakubwiye ibyazo. Ntibyashoboka ko hari intumwa yagira igitangaza ikora itabishobojwe na Allah. Ariko itegeko rya Allah (ry’ibihano) nirisohora, imanza zizacibwa mu kuri, kandi icyo gihe igihombo kizaba icy’abanyabinyoma"
  40,79,Allah ni we wabahaye amatungo kugira ngo mugire ayo mugendaho ndetse n’ayo murya
  40,80,Munayafiteho n’izindi nyungu nyinshi ndetse anabafasha kugera ku byo mwifuza mu mitima yanyu. Muyagendaho (ku butaka) nk’uko mugenda mu mato
  40,81,Anabereka ibimenyetso bye. Ese ni ibihe bimenyetso bya Allah muhakana
  40,82,"Ese (abahakanyi) ntibatambagira isi ngo barebe uko iherezo ry’abababanjirije ryagenze? Bari benshi kubarusha banabarusha imbaraga, ndetse banasize byinshi ku isi kubarusha; nyamara ibyo bakoraga ntacyo byabamariye"
  40,83,"Nuko ubwo bagerwagaho n’intumwa zabo zibazaniye ibimenyetso bigaragara, biratanye ubumenyi bari bafite, maze bagerwaho n’ibihano kubera ibyo bajyaga bakerensa"
  40,84,"Nuko babonye ibihano byacu, baravuga bati \"Twemeye Allah wenyine, kandi duhakanye ibyo twajyaga tumubangikanya nabyo"
  40,85,Ukwemera kwabo ntacyo kwabamariye nyuma yo kubona ibihano byacu. Uwo ni wo wari umugenzo wa Allah ku bagaragu be mu bihe byo hambere. Kandi icyo gihe igihombo cyabaye icy’abahakanyi (ubwo ibihano byacu byabageragaho)
  41,1,Haa Miim
  41,2,"(Iyi Qur’an) yahishuwe iturutse kwa (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  41,3,"Ni igitabo gifite imirongo yasesenguwe, gisomwa mu rurimi rw’Icyarabu ku bantu basobanukiwe (kuko ari bo babimenya bakanabishyira mu bikorwa)"
  41,4,"(Icyo gitabo) kivuga inkuru nziza ndetse kikanaburira, nyamara abenshi muri bo bagitera umugongo, bityo ntibumve (ngo bakemere)"
  41,5,"Baranavuga bati \"Imitima yacu iranangiye (ntishobora kumva) ibyo uduhamagarira, kandi n’amatwi yacu yarazibye ndetse hagati yacu nawe hari urusika, bityo kora ibyawe natwe dukore ibyacu"
  41,6,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Mu by’ukuri, njye ndi umuntu nka mwe, nahishuriwe ko Imana yanyu ari imwe rukumbi (Allah). Bityo, nimuyitunganire kandi muyicuzeho, (munamenye ko) ibihano bihambaye bizaba ku babangikanyamana"
  41,7,Ni babandi badatanga amaturo bakanahakana imperuka
  41,8,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza bazagororerwa ibihembo bihoraho"
  41,9,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ese mu by’ukuri, muhakana uwaremye isi mu minsi ibiri ndetse mukamubangikanya n’ibigirwamana? Uwo ni we Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose"
  41,10,"Yayishimangiyeho imisozi ndetse anayiha imigisha, anayigenaho ibitunga (ibinyabuzima) biyiriho mu minsi ine ingana 117. (Icyo ni cyo gisubizo) kubabaza (iby’iremwa ryayo)"
  41,11,"Hanyuma yerekeza ku kirere mu gihe cyari umwotsi, maze arakibwira cyo n’isi ati \"Nimuze mwembi, mwanze mukunze!\" Nuko biravuga biti \"Tuje duciye bugufi"
  41,12,"Abirema ari ibirere birindwi mu minsi ibiri, maze ahishurira buri kirere inshingano zacyo. Kandi ikirere kegereye isi twagitakishije amatara (inyenyeri), anakirinda (kuvogerwa namashitani). Uko ni ukugena kwa (Allah) Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  41,13,"Nibaramuka birengagije (ibyo ubabwira), uvuge uti \"Ndababurira (kuzagerwaho n’urusaku rw’) inkuba nk’urw’iyarimbuye aba Adi n’aba Thamudu"
  41,14,"Ubwo intumwa zabageragaho zibaturutse imbere n’inyuma, zirababwira ziti \"Ntimukagire indi mana musenga itari Allah\". Hanyuma bakavuga bati \"Iyo Nyagasani wacu ashaka (kutwoherereza intumwa) yari kohereza abamalayika. Rwose twe duhakanye ubwo butumwa (muvuga ko mwaje) mutuzaniye"
  41,15,"Naho aba Adi bagize ubwibone ku isi bitari mu kuri, maze baravuga bati \"Ni nde waturusha imbaraga?\" Ese ntibabona ko Allah wabaremye ari we ubarusha imbaraga? Kandi bahakanaga ibimenyetso byacu"
  41,16,"Nuko tuboherereza inkubi y’umuyaga uvuza ubuhuha mu minsi y’amakuba, kugira ngo tubasogongeze ku bihano bibasuzuguza mu buzima bwo ku isi. Kandi ibihano by’imperuka ni byo bizabasuzuguza kurushaho, ndetse ntibazanatabarwa"
  41,17,"N’aba Thamudu twabayoboye (inzira itunganye), ariko aho kuyoboka bahitamo kwirengagiza ukuri. Nuko bakubitwa n’inkuba nk’igihano gisuzuguritse cy’ibyo bakoraga"
  41,18,Maze turokora babandi bemeye kandi batinya Allah
  41,19,(Ubibutse) umunsi abanzi ba Allah bazakoranyirizwa hamwe; aba mbere n’aba nyuma nuko berekezwe mu muriro
  41,20,"Maze nibamara kuwugeraho, amatwi yabo n’amaso yabo ndetse n’imibiri yabo bizabashinja ibyo bajyaga bakora"
  41,21,"Nuko babwire imibiri yabo bati \"Kuki mwadushinje (ibyo twakoze)?\" Maze ivuge iti \" Allah wahaye buri kintu ubushobozi bwo kuvuga ni we watumye tuvuga. Kandi ni nawe wabaremye bwa mbere, ndetse iwe ni ho muzagarurwa"
  41,22,"Nta n’ubwo mwari gushobora guhisha (ibyo mwakoraga) amatwi yanyu, amaso yanyu, cyangwa imibiri yanyu kugira ngo bitazabashinja. Ahubwo mwibwiraga ko Allah atazi byinshi mu byo mukora"
  41,23,"Uko kwari ugukeka kwanyu mwakekeraga Nyagasani wanyu gutumye mworama, mukaba mubaye mu banyagihombo"
  41,24,"Bityo, nibashobora kwihangana, umuriro ni wo uzaba ubuturo bwabo, kandi nibasaba binginga kugarurwa ku isi, ntibazayigarurwaho"
  41,25,"Kandi twabateguriye inshuti magara (amashitani mu bantu no mu majini) zibakundisha (ibikorwa byabo bibi) mu buzima bwo ku isi, (zinabibagiza) ubuzima bw’imperuka. Maze bahamwa nijambo (ry’ibihano) nk’iryahamye amajini n’abantu babayeho mbere yabo. Mu by’ukuri, ni abanyagihombo"
  41,26,"Kandi babandi bahakanye (babwirana) bavuga bati \"Ntimukumve iyi Qur’an (igihe isomwa), ahubwo mujye muyirogoya kugira ngo mutsinde (Muhamadi)"
  41,27,"Ariko rwose babandi bahakanye tuzabasogongeza ibihano bikaze, kandi rwose tuzabahembera ibibi bakoraga"
  41,28,"Umuriro ni cyo gihembo cy’abanzi ba Allah, bazawubamo iteka, ari igihembo cy’uko bahakanaga amagambo yacu"
  41,29,"Kandi babandi bahakanye bazavuga bati \"Nyagasani wacu! Twereke abatuyobeje bo mu majini no mu bantu, maze tubashyire munsi y’ibirenge byacu kugira ngo basuzugurike"
  41,30,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bavuze bati \"Nyagasani wacu ni Allah\" hanyuma bagashikama (ku kuri), bazamanukirwa n’abamalayika (mu gihe cyabo cyo gupfa, bababwira bati) \"Mwigira ubwoba ndetse n’agahinda, ahubwo nimwakire inkuru nziza y’ijuru mwajyaga musezeranywa"
  41,31,"Twebwe turi inshuti zanyu mu buzima bwo ku isi ndetse n’ubwo ku mperuka. Kandi (mu ijuru) muzahabwamo ibyo imitima yanyu izifuza, ndetse murihabwemo ibyo muzasaba byose"
  41,32,"(Ibyo) bizaba ari izimano riturutse kuri (Allah) Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimbabazi"
  41,33,"Ni nde wavuga imvugo nziza kurusha wawundi uhamagarira (abantu) kugana Allah, kandi agakora ibikorwa byiza, nuko akavuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, njye ndi umwe mu bicisha bugufi\" (Abayisilamu)"
  41,34,"Kandi igikorwa cyiza n’ikibi ntibishobora kungana. Bityo, jya ukumira ikibi ukoresheje icyiza; ibyo bizatuma uwo mwari mufitanye urwango aba nk’inshuti yawe magara"
  41,35,"Ariko (ibyo) ntababihabwa usibye babandi bihangana, ndetse nta n’undi wabihabwa usibye umunyamahirwe ahambaye"
  41,36,"Kandi Shitani niramuka ishatse kugushuka, ujye wikinga kuri Allah. Mu by’ukuri, (Allah) ni we Uwumva bihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  41,37,"No mu bimenyetso bye (Allah) harimo ijoro n’amanywa, ndetse n’izuba n’ukwezi. Bityo, ntimukubamire izuba cyangwa ukwezi, ahubwo mujye mwubamira Allah we wabiremye, niba koko ari we wenyine musenga"
  41,38,"Ariko nibibona (bakanga gusenga Allah), (bamenye ko hari abamalayika) bari kwa Nyagasani wawe bamwambaza ijoro n’amanywa, batarambirwa na gato"
  41,39,"No mu bimenyetso bye (Allah) nuko ubona isi yumaganye, maze twayimanuraho amazi (imvura) ikanyeganyega ikanarumbuka, ndetse ikanameraho ibimera. Mu by’ukuri, uyiha ubuzima ni na we uzazura abapfuye. Rwose ni we ufite ubushobozi bwa buri kintu"
  41,40,"Mu by’ukuri, abagoreka amagambo yacu ntitubayobewe. Ese wawundi uzatabwa mu muriro ni we uzaba mwiza kurusha wawundi uzaza ku munsi w’imperuka atekanye? Ngaho nimukore ibyo mushaka. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni we ubona bihebuje ibyo mukora"
  41,41,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bahakanye urwibutso (Qur’an) ubwo rwabageragaho (tuzabahana). Kandi mu by’ukuri urwo (rwibutso) ni igitabo cyubashywe"
  41,42,"Nta makosa akirangwamo, yaba ari muri cyo cyangwa aturutse hanze yacyo. Ni igitabo cyahishuwe giturutse kwa (Allah) Umumenyi uhebuje, Ushimwa cyane"
  41,43,"Ntabyo ubwirwa (yewe Muhamadi) bitabwiwe intumwa zakubanjirije. Mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wawe ni Nyir’imbabazi, akaba na Nyir’ibihano bibabaza"
  41,44,"Kandi iyo (Qur’an) tuza kuyihishura mu rurimi rutari Icyarabu, (ababangikanyamana) bari kuvuga bati \"Kuki imirongo yayo idasobanutse (mu rurimi rwacu twumva)?\" (Allah ati) \"Ese (Qur’an) yaba itari mu Cyarabu (igasomwa) n’Umwarabu?\" Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"(Iyi Qur’an) ni umuyoboro ikaba n’umuti (ku bemeramana). Naho babandi batemera (Qur’an), amatwi yabo yarazibye kandi (Qur’an) kuri bo ni umwijima. Abo bameze nk’abahamagarirwa ahantu ha kure"
  41,45,"Kandi rwose Musa twamuhaye igitabo (Tawurati) ariko nticyavugwaho rumwe. N’iyo bitaza kuba ijambo riturutse kwa Nyagasani ryabanje (ryo kudahaniraho), bari guhita bacirwaho iteka (ryo kurimbuka). Mu by’ukuri, bo bari mu gushidikanya guteye amakenga"
  41,46,"Ukoze igikorwa cyiza aba acyikoreye, ndetse n’ukoze ikibi aba acyikoreye. Kandi Nyagasani wawe ntarenganya abagaragu be"
  41,47,"Ubumenyi bw’umunsi w’imperuka bwihariwe na we (Allah). Kandi nta mbuto zishobora gusohoka mu bishishwa byazo ngo zimere, ndetse nta n’ikigore cyatwita cyangwa ngo kibyare bitari mu bumenyi bwe. N’umunsi (Allah) azabahamagara agira ati \"Ibyo mwambangikanyaga nabyo birihe?\" Bazavuga bati \"Ubu turakumenyesha ko nta n’umwe muri twe waba umuhamya (ko ufite uwo mubangikanye)"
  41,48,Nuko ibyo basengaga mbere (ku isi) bizabatenguha. Icyo gihe ni bwo bazamenya ko nta buhungiro bafite
  41,49,"Umuntu ntajya arambirwa gusaba ibyiza, ariko iyo agezweho n’ikibi, ariheba agacika intege"
  41,50,"N’iyo tumusogongeje ku mpuhwe ziduturutseho nyuma yo kugerwaho n’ingorane, rwose aravuga ati \"Ibi mbibonye kuko mbikwiye, kandi sinkeka ko imperuka izabaho. Kandi nindamuka nsubijwe no kwa Nyagasani wanjye, mu by’ukuri, nzagirayo ibyiza kurushaho\". Rwose tuzabwira babandi bahakanye ibyo bakoze, ndetse tunabasogongeze ku bihano bikomeye"
  41,51,"Kandi iyo duhaye umuntu ingabire, yirengagiza (Nyagasani we akanga gushimira) akishyira hejuru, ariko ikibi cyamugeraho agatakamba cyane"
  41,52,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Nimumbwire! Ese niba (Qur’an) ituruka kwa Allah hanyuma mukaba muyihakana, ni nde waba warayobye kurusha wawundi uri mu mpaka ziri kure (y’ukuri)"
  41,53,"(Vuba aha) tuzabereka ibimenyetso byacu mu kirere ndetse no muri bo ubwabo, kugeza ubwo bagaragariwe ko iyi (Qur’an) ari ukuri. Ese ntibihagije kuba Nyagasani wawe ari we muhamya wa buri kintu"
  41,54,"Menya ko mu by’ukuri, (abahakanyi) bagishidikanya kuzahura na Nyagasani wabo. Menya ko mu by’ukuri, (Allah) ari we uzi neza buri kintu"
  42,1,Haa Miim
  42,2,A’in Siin Qaaf
  42,3,"Nk’uko Allah yaguhishuriye (Qur’an) ni nako yahishuriye abakubanjirije, akaba ari Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Ushishoza"
  42,4,"Ibiri mu birere n’ibiri mu isi ni ibye. Kandi ni we Uwikirenga, Uhambaye"
  42,5,"Ibirere byenda gusandara, kimwe hejuru y’ikindi (kubera igitinyiro cya Allah), abamalayika batagatifuza ishimwe rya Nyagasani wabo, bakanasabira imbabazi abari ku isi. Mumenye ko mu by’ukuri, Allah ari we Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimbabazi"
  42,6,"Na babandi bishyiriraho ibigirwamana baretse we, Allah ni we murinzi wabo, kandi wowe ntabwo ubashinzwe"
  42,7,"(Uko twaguhishuriye mbere, yewe Muhamadi) ni nako twaguhishuriye Qur’an iri mu rurimi rw’Icyarabu, kugira ngo uburire abatuye Umul Qura(Maka) n’abari mu nkengero zayo, kandi unaburire (abantu ibihano by’) umunsi w’ikoraniro udashidikanywaho. Ubwo itsinda rimwe rizaba riri mu ijuru, irindi riri mu muriro ugurumana"
  42,8,"N’iyo Allah aza kubishaka yari kubagira umuryango (umat) umwe (uyoboka idini rimwe), ariko yinjiza mu mpuhwe ze abo ashatse. Kandi abahakanyi ntibazagira umurinzi cyangwa umutabazi"
  42,9,"Ese (ababangikanyamana) bishyiriraho abarinzi mu cyimbo cya (Allah)? Nyamara Allah ni we Murinzi akaba ari na we uzura abapfuye, ndetse ni na we Ushoborabyose"
  42,10,"Kandi icyo ari cyo cyose mutavuzeho rumwe, itegeko ryacyo riba riri kwa Allah (mu gitabo cye). Uwo ni Allah, Nyagasani wanjye, ni we niringiye kandi ni nawe nicuzaho"
  42,11,"Umuhanzi w’ibirere n’isi; wabaremeye abagore ababakomoyemo, ndetse no mu matungo akaremamo ay’igitsina gabo n’igitsina gore; ni muri ubwo buryo mwororokamo. Ntagira icyo asa na cyo, kandi we ni Uwumva cyane, Ubona bihebuje"
  42,12,"Ni we nyir’imfunguzo z’ibiri mu birere no mu isi. Atuburira amafunguro uwo ashatse akanayatubiriza (uwo ashatse). Mu by’ukuri, ni Umumenyi wa byose"
  42,13,"Ibyo yabategetse mu idini ni nabyo yategetse Nuhu, ndetse n’ibyo twaguhishuriye (yewe Muhamadi), n’ibyo yategetse Ibrahimu, Musa na Issa, avuga ko mugomba gutunganya idini mwirinda kunyuranya naryo. Ababangikanyamana baremererwa n’ibyo mubahamagarira (byo gusenga Imana imwe). Allah yihitiramo uwo ashatse, Uwicuza. akanayobora inzira ye"
  42,14,"Kandi (abayoboke b’intumwa za mbere) batandukanye nyuma yo kugerwaho n’ubumenyi (Qur’an) bitewe no kugirirana ishyari n’inzangano. N’iyo bitaza kuba ijambo ryaturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe ryabanje ryo (kudahaniraho) kugeza igihe kizwi (imperuka), bari gucirwaho iteka (ryo kurimbuka). Mu by’ukuri, babandi bahawe igitabo (Tawurati na Injili) nyuma y’abo (bahakanyi) bagishidikanyaho mu buryo buteye amakenga"
  42,15,"Bityo, ibyo abe ari byo uhamagarira (abantu), kandi ukomeze utungane nk’uko wabitegetswe, ntuzanakurikire irari ryabo. Uvuge uti \"Nemera ibyo Allah yahishuye mu bitabo (byahawe intumwa), kandi nategetswe gukoresha ubutabera muri mwe. Allah ni we Nyagasani wacu akaba ari na we Nyagasani wanyu. Dufite ibikorwa byacu namwe mukagira ibyanyu. Nta mpaka zikwiye kuba hagati yacu na mwe. Allah azaduhuriza hamwe twese (aducire imanza). Kandi iwe ni ho garukiro (ryacu twese)"
  42,16,"Na babandi bajya impaka ku (idini rya) Allah nyuma y’uko iyobokwa (n’abantu), impaka zabo nta shingiro zifite kwa Nyagasani wabo. Bazagerwaho n’uburakari (bwa Allah), kandi bazahanishwa ibihano bikaze"
  42,17,Allah ni we wahishuye igitabo (gikubiyemo) ukuri n’ubutabera. Ese n’iki cyakubwira ko imperuka itari hafi
  42,18,"Ariko abatayemera (bifuza ko) yakwihutishwa, naho babandi bayemera barayitinya kandi bazi neza ko ari ukuri. Mumenye ko mu by’ukuri, abajya impaka ku mperuka bari mu buyobe bwa kure"
  42,19,"Allah agenza buhoro abagaragu be, aha amafunguro uwo ashatse kandi ni Umunyembaraga, Utsinda"
  42,20,"Ugamije gushaka ibihembo by’umunsi w’imperuka, tuzamwongerera ibihembo bye, n’ugamije gushaka ibihembo by’isi, tuzamuhaho ariko ku munsi w’imperuka nta mugabane azagira"
  42,21,"Ese (abahakanyi) baba bafite ibigirwamana byabashyiriyeho amategeko mu idini Allah atigeze ahera uburenganzira (abantu)? N’iyo bitaza kuba ijambo ryo kudahaniraho, bari gucirwaho iteka (ryo kurimbuka). Kandi mu by’ukuri, abahakanyi bazahanishwa ibihano bibabaza"
  42,22,"(Ku munsi w’imperuka) uzabona abahakanyi batewe ubwoba (n’ibihano) by’ibyo bakoze, kandi bigomba kubageraho nta kabuza. Nyamara babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, bazaba bari mu busitani bwo mu ijuru, bahabwa ibyo bashatse kwa Nyagasani wabo. Izo ni zo ngabire z’ikirenga"
  42,23,"Iyo ni yo nkuru nziza Allah aha abagaragu be bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza. Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"(Kubagezaho ubutumwa) simbibasabira igihembo (yemwe bantu ba Maka), usibye gusa urukundo rw’isano (mfitanye namwe). Kandi uzakora icyiza, tuzamutuburira (ibihembo) byacyo. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Ubabarira ibyaha, Ushima (ibikorwa by’abagaragu be)"
  42,24,"Bavuga ko (Muhamadi) yahimbiye Allah ikinyoma, ariko iyo Allah aza kubishaka yari kadanangira umutima wawe (iyo uramuka ubikoze). Kandi Allah akuraho ibitari ukuri agashimangiza ukuri amagambo ye. Mu by’ukuri, we ni Umumenyi uhebuje w’ibiri mu bituza (by’abantu)"
  42,25,"Ni nawe wakira ukwicuza kw’abagaragu be, akanababarira ibibi. Kandi azi neza ibyo mukora"
  42,26,"Yakira ubusabe bwa babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, ndetse akanabongerera mu ngabire ze. Kandi abahakanyi ibihano bikaze. bazahanishwa"
  42,27,"N’iyo Allah aza gutuburira amafunguro abagaragu be, bari kwigomeka ku isi, ariko abamanurira (amafunguro) ku rugero ashatse. Mu by’ukuri, azi kandi abona byimazeyo iby’abagaragu be (bakora)"
  42,28,"Ni na we umanura imvura nyuma y’uko (abantu) biheba, maze agasakaza impuhwe ze. Kandi ni Umurinzi, Ushimwa cyane"
  42,29,"No mu bimenyetso bye, ni iremwa ry’ibirere n’isi ndetse n’inyamaswa yakwirakwijemo. Kandi ashoboye kuzabakoranya igihe azashakira"
  42,30,Ikibi cyose kibageraho ni ingaruka z’ibyo mukora ubwanyu. Kandi (Allah) ababarira byinshi
  42,31,"Kandi ntabwo mwananira (Allah) ku isi, ndetse nta n’umurinzi cyangwa umutabazi mufite utari Allah"
  42,32,Na bimwe mu bimenyetso bye ni amato manini ameze nk’imisozi agendera mu nyanja
  42,33,"(Allah) aramutse abishatse yahagarika umuyaga, maze (amato) akaguma areremba hejuru yayo. Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo harimo ibimenyetso kuri buri wese wihangana cyane, unashimira"
  42,34,Cyangwa akayoreka kubera ibyo (ba nyir’amato) bakoze. Kandi (Allah) ababarira byinshi
  42,35,"Babandi bajya impaka ku magambo yacu, bazi neza ko nta buhungiro bazagira"
  42,36,"Icyo muhawe cyose mu buzima bw’isi, kiba ari umunezero w’igihe gito, naho ibiri kwa Allah ni byo byiza kandi bizahoraho kuri babandi bemeye bakaniringira Nyagasani wabo"
  42,37,"Na babandi birinda ibyaha bikomeye n’ibiteye isoni, kandi barakara bakababarira"
  42,38,"Na babandi bumvira Nyagasani wabo, bagahozaho amasengesho, bakajya inama ku byo bakora, ndetse bakanatanga mu byo twabahaye"
  42,39,Ndetse na babandi bitabara igihe bagiriwe akarengane
  42,40,"Kandi inyiturano y’ikibi ni ikibi nka cyo, ariko ubabariye akaniyunga (n’uwamugiriye nabi), uwo ibihembo bye biri kwa Allah. Mu by’ukuri, (Allah) ntakunda abarenganya abandi"
  42,41,"Naho abazitabara nyuma yo kurenganywa, abo nta nkurikizi zizababaho"
  42,42,Ahubwo abo inkurikizi zizabaho ni babandi barenganya abantu bakanakora ubwangizi ku isi. Abo bazahanishwa ibihano bibabaza
  42,43,"Kandi uzihangana akanababarira, mu by’ukuri ibyo biri mu butwari bukomeye"
  42,44,"N’uwo Allah arekeye mu buyobe, nta wundi utari we (Allah) wamutabara (ngo amuyobore). Kandi (wowe Muhamadi) uzabona inkozi z’ibibi ubwo zizaba zibonye ibihano zikavuga ziti \"Ese hari uburyo twasubira ku isi"
  42,45,"Kandi uzababona bajyanywe mu muriro, baciye bugufi basuzuguritse, bahengereza umuriro. Maze babandi bemeye bavuge bati \"Rwose abanyagihombo nyabo ku munsi w’imperuka, ni abivukije (kujya mu ijuru) bakanarivutsa imiryango yabo\". Mumenye ko rwose inkozi z’ibibi zizahanishwa ibihano bihoraho"
  42,46,Kandi ntibazagira ababarinda (ibihano) batari Allah. N’uwo Allah arekeye mu buyobe nta buryo yabuvamo
  42,47,Nimwumvire Nyagasani wanyu mbere y’uko mugerwaho numunsi udasubizwa inyuma wagenwe na Allah. Kuri uwo munsi nta buhungiro muzagira ndetse nta n’ubwo muzashobora guhakana (ibyaha mwakoze)
  42,48,"Ariko nibaramuka birengagije (kumvira Allah), umenye ko (yewe Muhamadi) tutakohereje kuba umugenzuzi (w’ibikorwa byabo); ahubwo icyo ushinzwe ni ugusohoza ubutumwa. Kandi mu by’ukuri, iyo dusogongeje umuntu ku byiza biduturutseho, arabyishimira; ariko bagerwaho n’ikibi kubera ibyo bakoze (bagahita bibanda ku bibi byabagezeho). Mu by’ukuri, umuntu ni indashima"
  42,49,"Ubwami bw’ibirere n’ubw’isi ni ubwa Allah wenyine. Arema ibyo ashatse. Aha impano (yo kubyara) abakobwa uwo ashatse, ndetse akanaha impano yo kubyara abahungu uwo ashatse"
  42,50,"Cyangwa akabagenera kubyara abahungu n’abakobwa, ndetse uwo ashatse akamwima urubyaro. Mu by’ukuri, (Allah) ni Umumenyi uhebuje, Ushobora byose"
  42,51,"Ntibibaho ko Allah yavugisha umuntu bitanyuze mu guhishurirwa cyangwa kumva ijwi rimuvugisha, cyangwa (Allah) yabishaka akamwoherereza intumwa ikamuhishurira ibyo (Allah) ashaka. Mu by’ukuri, (Allah) ni Uwikirenga, Ushishoza"
  42,52,"(Nk’uko twahishuriye intumwa zakubanjirije, yewe Muhamadi) ni nako twaguhishuriye Qur’an ku bw’itegeko ryacu. Mbere yo guhishurirwa ntabwo wari uzi igitabo (Qur’an), ndetse nta n’ubwo wari usobanukiwe ukwemera. Ariko (Qur’an) twayigize urumuri tuyoboresha abo dushaka mu bagaragu bacu. Mu by’ukuri, wowe uyobora (abantu) inzira igororotse"
  42,53,"Inzira ya Allah, we Mugenga w’ibiri mu birere n’ibiri ku isi. Mumenye ko kwa Allah ari ho ibintu byose bizasubira. Yahishuriwe i Maka, ig"
  43,1,Haa Miim
  43,2,Ndahiriye ku gitabo gisobanutse
  43,3,"Mu by’ukuri, (icyo gitabo) twakigize Qur’an iri mu rurimi rw’icyarabu kugira ngo mubashe gusobanukirwa"
  43,4,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, iyo (Qur’an) iri mu gitabo gihatse ibindi byose (Lawuhu Mahfudh), ifite agaciro gakomeye kandi yuje ubuhanga"
  43,5,"Nonese tubihorere, nuko tureke guhishura urwibutso (Qur’an), kubera ko muri abantu b’inkozi z’ibibi (mwanze kurwemera)"
  43,6,Ese ni abahanuzi bangahe twohereje mu babayeho mbere yawe (yewe Muhamadi)
  43,7,Nta muhanuzi n’umwe wabageragaho ngo babure kumunnyega
  43,8,"Nuko turimbura abari abanyembaraga kubarusha (abahakanyi b’i Maka), kandi urugero rw’abo tworetse mbere rwaratambutse"
  43,9,"Kandi iyo ubabajije uti \"Ni nde waremye ibirere n’isi\"? Rwose baravuga bati \"Byaremwe na (Allah) Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  43,10,"We wabashyiriyeho isi ishashe, akanabashyiriraho amayira kugira ngo muyanyuremo mugere ku ntego zanyu"
  43,11,"Ni nawe wamanuye amazi mu kirere ku gipimo kiri mu rugero, nuko tuyahesha ubuzima ubutaka bwapfuye. Ndetse uko ni ko muzazurwa"
  43,12,Ni nawe waremye amoko y’ibiremwa bitandukanye. Yanabashyiriyeho amato n’amatungo mugendaho
  43,13,"Kugira ngo mwicare hejuru yayo, maze muzirikane ingabire za Nyagasani wanyu muvuga muti \"Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Allah, we watworohereje ibi; kandi ntitwari kubyishoborera"
  43,14,Kandi kwa Nyagasani wacu ni ho tuzasubira
  43,15,"(Ababangikanyamana) bafashe bamwe mu bagaragu ba Allah (abamalayika) babita abakobwa be. Mu by’ukuri, umuntu ni indashima ku buryo bugaragara"
  43,16,"Ese (Allah) yakwigenera mu biremwa bye abakobwa120, maze mwe akabaha umwihariko w’abahungu"
  43,17,"N’iyo umwe muri bo ahawe inkuru y’ibyo yitiriye Allah Nyirimpuhwe (yo kubyara umukobwa), uburanga bwe burijima akarakara"
  43,18,"Ese uwabyirukiye mu mitako, nyamara akaba atabasha kujya impaka mu bikomeye (ni we bitirira Allah)"
  43,19,Kandi bafashe abamalayika babita abagore nyamara ari abagaragu ba Allah Nyirimpuhwe. Ese mu iremwa ryabo bari bahari? Ubuhamya bwabo (bw’ikinyoma) buzandikwa kandi bazabibazwa
  43,20,"Baranavuze bati \"Iyo Allah Nyirimpuhwe aza kubishaka ntitwari gusenga ibigirwamana\". Ibyo bavuga nta bumenyi babifitiye, ahubwo barabeshya"
  43,21,Ese twaba twarabahaye igitabo mbere yayo (Qur’an) bakaba ari cyo bashingiraho (ibyo bavuga)
  43,22,"Ahubwo baravuga bati \"Mu by’ukuri, twasanze abakurambere bacu ari yo nzira barimo, bityo natwe turabakurikira"
  43,23,"Uko ni nako byagenze mbere, nta muhanuzi n’umwe twohereje mu mudugudu mbere yawe (wowe Muhamadi), ngo ibikomerezwa byawo bibure kuvuga biti \"Mu by’ukuri, twasanze abakurambere bacu ari yo nzira barimo (yo gusenga ibigirwamana), bityo natwe turabigana"
  43,24,"(Uwo muhanuzi) akababwira ati \"Ese n’iyo naba mbazaniye inzira iruta iyo mwasanganye abakurambere banyu (mwampakana)?\" Baravuga bati \"Mu by’ukuri, ibyo mutuzaniye turabihakanye"
  43,25,"Nuko turabibahanira. Bityo, nimurebe uko iherezo ry’abahinyuye ukuri ryagenze"
  43,26,"Kandi wibuke ubwo Ibrahimu yabwiraga se ndetse n’abantu be ati \"Mu by’ukuri, njye nitandukanyije nibyo musenga"
  43,27,"Usibye uwampanze (ni we nzasenga wenyine), kuko ari we uzanyobora"
  43,28,"Maze iryo jambo (ryo gusenga Allah wenyine) Ibrahimu ariraga abazamukomokaho, kugira ngo bagarukire (Allah)"
  43,29,Ariko abo (babangikanyamana) n’ababyeyi babo twabahaye umunezero w’igihe gito kugeza ubwo bagezweho n’ukuri ndetse n’intumwa ibasobanurira
  43,30,"Nuko bamaze kugerwaho n’ukuri baravuze bati \"Ubu ni uburozi kandi turabuhakanye"
  43,31,"Baranavuze bati \"Iyo iyi Quran (iba ari ukuri),yariguhishurirwa umugabo w’igikomerezwa ukomoka muri umwe mu mijyi ibiri (Maka na Twaifu)"
  43,32,"Ese ni bo bagaba impuhwe (ubutumwa) za Nyagasani wawe (aho bihitiyemo)? Ahubwo ni twe twabagabiye imibereho yabo mu buzima bw’iyi si. Tunazamura mu ntera bamwe muri bo, kugira ngo bamwe bakorere abandi (imirimo). Kandi impuhwe za Nyagasani wawe ni zo nziza kuruta izo bakusanya"
  43,33,"Kandi n’iyo abantu baza kuba umuryango umwe (w’abahakanyi), twari guha abahakana Allah Nyirimpuhwe, inzu zifite ibisenge bya feza n’ingazi buririraho"
  43,34,N’amazu yabo tukayaha inzugi n’intebe zegamirwaho (byose bya Feza)
  43,35,Ndetse n’imitako (ya Zahabu). Nyamara ibyo byose ni umunezero w’igihe gito cy’ubuzima bwo kuri iyi si. Kandi ubuzima bwo ku munsi w’imperuka kwa Nyagasani wawe ni ubw’abatinya Allah
  43,36,"Kandi uzirengagiza urwibutso rwa Allah Nyirimpuhwe, tuzamugira ingaruzwamuheto ya Shitani, maze imubere inshuti (magara)"
  43,37,"Mu by’ukuri, (shitani) zibakumira kugana inzira igororotse, bakanibwira ko ari bo bayobotse"
  43,38,"Kugeza ubwo (uwirengagije urwibutso) azatugeraho (akerekwa iherezo rye ribi), maze abwire (shitani yamuyobeje) ati \"Iyo hagati yanjye na we haza kuba hari intera ingana nk’iri hagati y’iburasirazuba n’uburengerazuba (simbe narakugize inshuti). Mbega ukuntu wambereye inshuti mbi"
  43,39,"Maze (babwirwe bati) \"Ntacyo (ukwicuza kwanyu) uyu munsi kwabamarira kuko mwakoze ibibi, mu by’ukuri, murafatanya ibihano"
  43,40,Ese wowe ushobora kumvisha igipfamatwi cyangwa ukayobora impumyi ndetse n’uri mu buyobe bugaragara
  43,41,"N’ubwo twakujyana (ugapfa mbere y’uko ubona ibihano byabo tuzabahanisha, wowe Muhamadi), mu by’ukuri, tuzabaryoza (ibyo bakoze)"
  43,42,"Cyangwa tukakwereka (ibihano) twabasezeranyije. Mu by’ukuri, twe tubafiteho ubushobozi"
  43,43,"Bityo (yewe Muhamadi), komeza ushikame ku byo wahishuriwe. Mu by’ukuri, uri mu nzira igororotse"
  43,44,Mu by’ukuri (iyi Qur’an) ni urwibutso kuri wowe no ku bantu bawe kandi muzayibazwa
  43,45,"Kandi unabaze mu bo twohereje mbere yawe mu ntumwa zacu, niba twaba twarashyizeho ibigirwamana bisengwa mu cyimbo cya (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe"
  43,46,"Kandi rwose twahaye Musa ibitangaza byacu tumwohereza kwa Farawo n’ibyegera bye (kugira ngo abahamagarire kuyoboka inzira igororotse). Nuko (Musa) aravuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, njye ndi intumwa ya Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose"
  43,47,"Ariko ubwo yabageragaho azanye ibitangaza byacu, baramusetse barabinnyega"
  43,48,"Kandi buri gitangaza twerekaga (Farawo n’abantu be) cyabaga (kigaragaza ukuri kwa Mussa) kuruta kigenzi cyacyo cya kibanjirije (ariko byose barabihakanye), maze tubahanisha ibihano bihambaye kugira ngo bagarukire (Allah)"
  43,49,"Nuko babwira (Musa) bati \"Yewe wa murozi we! Dusabire Nyagasani wawe ku bw’isezerano yaguhaye. Mu by’ukuri (naramuka adukijije ibihano) rwose turayoboka"
  43,50,"Maze tubakijije ibihano, bica isezerano"
  43,51,"Nuko Farawo ahamagara abantu be, agira ati \"Yemwe bantu banjye! Ese sinjye nyir’ubwami bwa Misiri n’iyi migezi itemba munsi (y’ingoro) yanjye? Ese ntimubona"
  43,52,"Ese sinjye muntu mwiza kuruta uyu (Musa) usuzuguritse, udashobora no kwisobanura"
  43,53,"Kuki atamanuriwe ibikomo bya zahabu, cyangwa ngo aze aherekejwe n’abamalayika (bo kumushyigikira)"
  43,54,"Nuko (Farawo) aba ahinduye abantu be abasazi arabayobya maze baramwumvira. Mu by’ukuri, bari abantu b’inkozi z’ibibi"
  43,55,"Nuko bamaze kuturakaza twarihoreye, maze tubaroha (mu mazi) bose"
  43,56,Nuko tubagira icyitegererezo n’iciro ry’umugani (ngo babe isomo) ku bazaza nyuma
  43,57,"Kandi ubwo (ababangikanyamana) batangagaho urugero121 mwene Mariyamu (Issa), icyo gihe abantu bawe (yewe Muhamadi) bararwishimiye"
  43,58,"Maze baravuga bati \"Ese imana zacu ni zo z’ukuri cyangwa we (Yesu ni we w’ukuri)?\" Urwo rugero baguhaye byari ukukugisha impaka gusa. Ahubwo ni abantu bakunda kujya impaka no guhakana"
  43,59,"(Yesu) nta kindi yari cyo usibye ko yari umugaragu wacu twahaye ingabire (y’ubutumwa), kandi tumugira igitangaza kuri bene Isiraheli"
  43,60,Iyo tuza kubishaka (yemwe bantu) twari kubasimbuza abamalayika basimburana ku isi
  43,61,"Mu by’ukuri, (kugaruka kwa Issa) ni ikimenyetso cy’imperuka. Bityo, ntimukagishidikanyeho ahubwo nimunkurikire. Iyo ni yo nzira itunganye"
  43,62,"Kandi rwose Shitani ntikabakumire (kugana iyo nzira), kuko mu by’ukuri, ari umwanzi wanyu ugaragara"
  43,63,"Maze ubwo Issa yazaniraga (bene Isiraheli) ibitangaza, arababwira ati \"Rwose mbazaniye ubutumwa ndetse no kugira ngo mbasobanurire bimwe mutavugaho rumwe. Ngaho nimutinye Allah kandi munyumvire"
  43,64,"Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni we Nyagasani wanjye akaba ari na we Nyagasani wanyu, ngaho nimumusenge. Iyi niyo nzira itunganye"
  43,65,Nuko amatsinda (mu bahawe igitabo) ntiyavuga rumwe (ku nkuru ya Issa). Bityo ibihano bikaze ku munsi ubabaza (imperuka) bizaba ku nkozi z’ibibi (zihimbira Yesu ibinyoma)
  43,66,Ese hari ikindi bategereje kitari ukugerwaho n’imperuka ibatunguye batabizi
  43,67,"Kuri uwo munsi abari inshuti magara bazaba abanzi, usibye gusa abatinya (Allah)"
  43,68,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Bagaragu banjye! Uyu munsi ntimugire ubwoba ndetse n’agahinda"
  43,69,Babandi bemeye amagambo yacu kandi bakicisha bugufi (bakaba Abayisilamu)
  43,70,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Nimwinjire mu Ijuru, mwe n’abagore banyu munezerewe"
  43,71,"Bazazengurutswamo amasahane n’ibikombe bya zahabu (birimo ibiribwa n’ibinyobwa byiza), kandi muri ryo (Ijuru) bazabonamo ibishimishije kandi biryoheye amaso, muzanaribamo ubuziraherezo"
  43,72,"(Babwirwe bati) \"Ngiryo Ijuru murazwe kubera ibyo mwakoraga"
  43,73,Muzahabwamo imbuto nyinshi muzajya murya
  43,74,"Mu by’ukuri, inkozi z’ibibi zizaba mu muriro wa Jahanama ubuziraherezo"
  43,75,"Ntibazigera boroherezwa (ibihano by’umuriro), kandi bazawubamo bihebye"
  43,76,"Nta n’ubwo twigeze tubarenganya, ahubwo bari inkozi z’ibibi"
  43,77,"Kandi (inkozi z’ibibi) zizatakamba zigira ziti \"Yewe Maliki (Malayika urinda umuriro)! (Tubwirire) Nyagasani wawe adukureho burundu\". Azavuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, muzabamo ubuziraherezo"
  43,78,Rwose twabazaniye ukuri ariko abenshi muri mwe banze ukuri
  43,79,"Cyangwa banogeje umugambi mubisha (wo kugirira nabi Intumwa Muhamadi)? Mu by’ukuri, ni twe twemeza ikigomba gukorwa"
  43,80,Cyangwa bakeka ko tutumva amabanga yabo n’ibyo bongorerana? Yego (turabyumva rwose)! Kandi n’intumwa zacu (abamalayika) ziba ziri hafi yabo zandika
  43,81,"Vuga uti \"Niba (Allah) Nyirimbabazi yaragize umwana (nk’uko mubivuga), njye nari kuba uwa mbere mu bamusenga"
  43,82,"Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Nyagasani w’ibirere n’isi, Nyagasani Nyir’intebe y’icyubahiro! Ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamwitirira"
  43,83,"Bareke bavuge ibidafite umumaro, banikinire kugeza ubwo bazahura n’umunsi wabo basezeranyijwe"
  43,84,"Ni we (Allah) Mana yonyine mu kirere, ndetse ni na we Mana yonyine ku isi. Kandi ni nawe Ushishoza, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  43,85,"Ubutagatifu ni ubw’ufite ubwami bw’ibirere n’isi ndetse n’ibiri hagati yabyo. Ni nawe uzi iby’imperuka, kandi ni nawe muzagarurwaho"
  43,86,"Naho ibyo basenga bitari we, nta bushobozi bifite bwo kubakorera ubuvugizi, usibye babandi bahamije ukuri kandi babizi (ni bo bazakorerwa ubuvugizi)"
  43,87,"Kandi uramutse ubabajije uwabaremye, rwose bavuga bati \" Allah\". Nonese ni gute bateshwa (gusenga Allah wabaremye)"
  43,88,"(Kandi Allah azi) imvugo ye (Muhamadi) igira iti \"Nyagasani wanjye! Mu by’ukuri, aba ni abantu batemera"
  43,89,"Bityo, bababarire unavuge uti \"Salamu (Amahoro) !\" Rwose bidatinze bazamenya (iherezo ry’ubuhakanyi bwabo). Yahishuriwe i Maka, ig Ku izina rya Allah, Nyiri"
  44,1,Haa Miim
  44,2,Ndahiriye ku gitabo (Qur’an) gisobanutse
  44,3,"Mu by’ukuri, twakimanuye mu ijoro ryuje imigisha (Laylat-ul Qadri). Rwose turi ababurizi (b’uko ibihano bizashyikira abahakanyi)"
  44,4,"Muri iryo (joro) ni bwo buri kintu (kizaba mu mwaka) kigenwa (amafunguro, igihe cy’amavuko, igihe cyo gupfa, amakuba)"
  44,5,"Ni iteka riduturutseho. Mu by’ukuri, ni twe twohereza (intumwa)"
  44,6,"Ku bw’impuhwe ziturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe. Mu by’ukuri, (Allah) ni Uwumva bihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  44,7,Nyagasani w’ibirere n’isi ndetse n’ibiri hagati yabyo; niba muri abizera b’ukuri (nimube ariwe musenga wenyine)
  44,8,Nta yindi mana iriho itari we (Allah). Ni we utanga ubuzima n’urupfu. Ni Nyagasani wanyu akaba ari na we Nyagasani w’abakurambere banyu
  44,9,Nyamara bo bari mu gushidikanya bikinira
  44,10,Ngaho tegereza umunsi ikirere kizazana umwotsi ugaragara
  44,11,Uzapfukirana abantu. Icyo ni igihano kibabaza
  44,12,"(Bazavuga bati) \"Nyagasani wacu! Dukize ibihano! Mu by’ukuri, turaba abemera"
  44,13,"Ni gute bakwibuka kwemera (ubu), kandi bari baragezweho n’intumwa (Muhamadi) ibasobanurira"
  44,14,"Maze bakayitera umugongo, bakavuga bati \"Uyu ni umuntu wigishijwe (n’abandi) kandi ni umusazi"
  44,15,"Rwose turabakuriraho ibihano mu gihe gito, kandi nta kabuza muzongera musubire (mu buhakanyi)"
  44,16,"Umunsi tuzabahanisha igihano gikomeye. Mu by’ukuri, tuzabaryoza (ibyo bakoze)"
  44,17,"Kandi mbere yabo (ababangikanyamana) twagerageje abantu ba Farawo, ubwo intumwa yubahitse (Musa) yabageragaho"
  44,18,"(Irababwira iti) \"Nimumpe abagaragu ba Allah (mbajyane). Mu by’ukuri, njye ndi intumwa yizewe iboherejwemo"
  44,19,Ntimukanishyire hejuru imbere ya Allah. Rwose mbazaniye ibimenyetso bigaragara
  44,20,"Kandi nikinze kuri Nyagasani wanjye ari na we Nyagasani wanyu, kugira ngo mutantera amabuye"
  44,21,Ariko nimutananyemera mundeke (ntimungirire nabi)
  44,22,"(Nuko bashaka kumugirira nabi) maze atakambira Nyagasani we agira ati \"Mu by’ukuri, aba bantu ni abagizi ba nabi (ubandinde)"
  44,23,"(Allah aramubwira ati) \"Ujyane n’abagaragu banjye nijoro; rwose (Farawo n’ingabo ze) baraza kubakurikira"
  44,24,"(Nimumara kwambuka) ureke inyanja igume uko iri ituje. Mu by’ukuri, (Farawo n’ingabo ze) baraza kurohama"
  44,25,(Ese Farawo n’abantu be) basize ubusitani n’imigezi bingana iki
  44,26,Ibihingwa n’amazu meza
  44,27,Naho umudendezo babagamo banezerewe
  44,28,Uko ni ko byagenze! (Imitungo yabo) twayizunguje abandi bantu
  44,29,Ikirere n’isi ntibyigeze bibaririra123 kandi ntibigeze bakererezwa (guhanwa)
  44,30,Kandi rwose twarokoye bene Isiraheli ibihano bisuzuguza
  44,31,"Bya Farawo, wari warishyize hejuru akaba n’umwangizi"
  44,32,(Bene Isiraheli) twabatoranyije tubizi tubarutisha ibiremwa (byo ku gihe cyabo)
  44,33,Twanabahaye ibitangaza birimo ibigeragezo bigaragara
  44,34,"Mu by’ukuri, abo (bahakanyi b’i Maka) baravuga bati"
  44,35,"Rwose nta rundi rupfu ruzabaho usibye urupfu rwacu rwa mbere (abantu bose bapfa), ndetse nta n’ubwo tuzazurwa"
  44,36,Ngaho nimugarure abakurambere bacu (bapfuye kera) niba muvuga ukuri (ko Allah azazura abapfuye)
  44,37,"Ese abo (babangikanyamana) nibo beza cyangwa se abantu ba Tubba’i124, ndetse na babandi babayeho mbere yabo? (Abo bose) twaraboretse kubera ko bari abagizi ba nabi"
  44,38,Ntabwo twaremye ibirere n’isi ndetse n’ibiri hagati yabyo dukina
  44,39,Nta kindi cyatumye tubirema uretse ku mpamvu z’ukuri; nyamara abenshi muri bo ntibabizi
  44,40,"Mu by’ukuri, umunsi w’urubanza (ubwo Allah azakiranura ibiremwa), ni wo munsi w’isezerano rya bose"
  44,41,"Umunsi inshuti magara itazagira icyo imarira inshuti magara ngenzi yayo, ndetse nta n’ubwo bazatabarwa"
  44,42,"Uretse uwo Allah azagirira impuhwe. Mu by’ukuri, (Allah) ni Umunyembaraga uhebuje, Nyirimbabazi"
  44,43,"Mu by’ukuri, igiti cya Zaqumu"
  44,44,Kizaba amafunguro y’abanyabyaha
  44,45,"(Ayo mafunguro azaba ameze) nk’umuringa washongeshejwe, uzaba utogotera mu nda"
  44,46,Nko gutogota kw’amazi yatuye
  44,47,"(Hazatangwa itegeko rigira riti) \"Nimumufate mumukururire rwagati mu muriro uguramana"
  44,48,Maze mumusuke mu mutwe amazi yatuye nk’igihano
  44,49,"(Maze abwirwe ati) \"Sogongera! Mu by’ukuri, (wajyaga wibwira ko) uri umunyembaraga ukaba n’umunyacyubahiro"
  44,50,"Mu by’ukuri, iki ni cyo (gihano) mwajyaga mushidikanyaho"
  44,51,"Mu by’ukuri, abatinya Allah bazaba bari ahantu hatekanye (mu Ijuru)"
  44,52,Mu busitani n’imigezi
  44,53,"Bazaba bambaye imyambaro ikoze mu ihariri yorohereye ndetse n’iremereye, barebana"
  44,54,"Uko ni ko bizaba bimeze. Tuzanabashyingira Huur ul-a’in (abagore bo mu Ijuru b’igikundiro, b’amaso manini)"
  44,55,"Bazarihererwamo imbuto (z’ubwoko bwose), batekanye"
  44,56,"Ntabwo bazasogongeramo urupfu uretse urupfu rwa mbere (bari ku isi), kandi Allah azabarinda ibihano by’umuriro ugurumana"
  44,57,Bizaba ari ingabire ziturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe! Iyo ni yo izaba ari intsinzi ihambaye
  44,58,"Mu by’ukuri, (Qur’an) twarayoroheje mu rurimi rwawe (rw’Icyarabu), kugira ngo bibuke (maze bibabere isomo)"
  44,59,"Ngaho (yewe Muhamadi) tegereza (ibyo nagusezeranyije bizababaho), mu by’ukuri nabo bategereje (ibizakubaho)"
  45,1,Haa Miim
  45,2,"Ihishurwa ry’iki gitabo (Qur’an) rituruka kwa Allah, Umunyembaraga uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  45,3,"Mu by’ukuri, (ukuremwa) kw’ibirere n’isi ni ibimenyetso ku bemeramana"
  45,4,"No mu iremwa ryanyu ndetse n’uburyo (Allah) akwirakwiza inyamaswa (ku isi), ni ibimenyetso ku bantu bemera badashidikanya"
  45,5,"No mu gusimburana kw’ijoro n’amanywa ndetse n’amafunguro (imvura) Allah amanura mu kirere, akayahesha isi ubuzima nyuma yo gupfa kwayo (gukakara), ndetse n’ihindagurika ry’imiyaga; ni ibimenyetso ku bantu bafite ubwenge"
  45,6,Ayo ni amagambo ya Allah tugusomera mu kuri (yewe Muhamadi). Ese ni ayahe magambo yandi bakemera nyuma y’amagambo ya Allah ndetse n’ibimenyetso bye
  45,7,"Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri buri wese uhimba ibinyoma, w’umunyabyaha"
  45,8,"Wawundi usomerwa amagambo ya Allah, maze agatsimbarara, agatera umugongo yibona nk’aho atayumvise. (Yewe Muhamadi) muhe inkuru y’ibihano bibabaza"
  45,9,N’iyo hari icyo amenye mu magambo yacu arayacyerensa. Abo bazahanishwa ibihano bisuzuguza
  45,10,"Kandi n’imbere yabo hari umuriro wa Jahanamu, kandi ibyo bakoze cyangwa izindi mana bishyiriyeho zitari Allah ntacyo bizabamarira. Ndetse bazahanishwa ibihano bihambaye"
  45,11,(Iyi Qur’an) ni wo muyoboro. Naho babandi bahakanye amagambo ya Nyagasani wabo bazahanishwa ibihano bibi cyane kandi bibabaza
  45,12,"Allah ni we waborohereje inyanja kugira ngo amato ayigendemo ku itegeko rye, no kugira ngo mushakishe ingabire gushimira. ze ndetse munabashe"
  45,13,"Yanaborohoreje ibiri mu birere n’ibiri mu isi byose bimuturutseho. Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo hari ibimenyetso ku bantu batekereza"
  45,14,"(Yewe Muhamadi!) Bwira abemeye bababarire babandi badatinya iminsi ya Allah (azabahaniraho kubera ibibi bakora), kugira ngo azagororere abantu ibyo bakoraga"
  45,15,"Ukoze ibikorwa byiza aba abyikoreye, ndetse n’ukoze ikibi aba acyikoreye. Hanyuma kwa Nyagasani wanyu ni ho muzasubizwa"
  45,16,"Kandi rwose twahaye bene Isiraheli igitabo, ubushishozi n’ubuhanuzi. Twanabahaye amafunguro meza, tunabarutisha ibiremwa (byo ku gihe cyabo)"
  45,17,Ndetse twabahaye amategeko asobanutse. Kandi batandukanye nyuma yo kugerwaho n’ubumenyi bitewe no kugirirana ishyari n’inzangano hagati yabo. Rwose Nyagasani wawe azabakiranura ku munsi w’imperuka mu byo batavugagaho rumwe
  45,18,"Hanyuma (yewe Muhamadi) tugushyira ku murongo w’amategeko y’idini (asobanutse). Bityo, wukurikire kandi ntuzakurikire irari ry’abadasobanukiwe"
  45,19,"Mu by’ukuri, ntacyo bakumarira imbere ya Allah (aramutse ashatse kuguhana). Rwose bamwe mu nkozi z’ibibi ni inshuti magara z’abandi, ariko Allah ni umukunzi w’abamwubaha"
  45,20,"Iyi (Qur’an) ni urumuri ku bantu, ikaba umuyoboro n’impuhwe ku bizera badashidikanya"
  45,21,Ese abakora ibibi bakeka ko twabafata kimwe n’abemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza; haba mu mibereho yabo yo ku isi ndetse na nyuma yo gupfa? Rwose ibyo bibwira si ukuri
  45,22,"Kandi Allah yaremye ibirere n’isi mu kuri, no kugira ngo buri muntu azahemberwe ibyo yakoze, kandi ntibazigera barenganywa"
  45,23,"Ese ntiwabonye wawundi wagize irari rye nk’imana ye, maze Allah akamurekera mu buyobe abizi neza (ko azayoba), nuko akamuziba amatwi, akadanangira umutima we, ndetse akanashyira igikingirizo ku maso ye? Ese nyuma ya Allah ni nde wundi wamuyobora? Mbese ubu ntimushobora kwibuka"
  45,24,"Kandi baravuze bati \"Ubuzima nta kindi buri cyo usibye kuba ku isi, tugapfa tukanabaho, kandi nta kindi kitworeka kitari igihe. Ibyo nta bumenyi babifitiye, usibye gukeka gusa"
  45,25,"N’iyo basomewe amagambo yacu asobanutse, urwitwazo rwabo ruba kuvuga bati \"Ngaho nimugarure abakurambere bacu niba muvuga ukuri (ko Allah azazura abapfuye)"
  45,26,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \" Allah ni we ubaha ubuzima hanyuma akabubambura (igihe cyo gupfa), maze akazabakoranya ku munsi w’imperuka, (umunsi) udashidikanywaho. Nyamara abenshi mu bantu ntibabizi"
  45,27,"Ubwami bw’ibirere n’ubw’isi ni ubwa Allah wenyine, kandi umunsi w’imperuka nugera, kuri uwo munsi abanyabinyoma bazahomba"
  45,28,"(Ku munsi w’imperuka) uzanabona buri muryango (Umat) upfukamye, na buri muryango uhamagarwa ngo ujye (gusoma) igitabo cyawo (cy’ibikorwa, maze babwirwe bati) \"Uyu munsi murahemberwa ibyo mwajyaga mukora"
  45,29,Iki gitabo cyacu kibavugaho ukuri. Rwose twandikaga ibyo mwajyaga mukora (byose)
  45,30,"Naho abemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, Nyagasani wabo azabinjiza mu mpuhwe ze (Ijuru). Iyo ni yo ntsinzi igaragara"
  45,31,"Naho babandi bahakanye (babwirwe bati) \"Ese ntimwasomerwaga amagambo yacu? Nyamara mwishyize hejuru maze muba abagizi ba nabi"
  45,32,"N’iyo mubwiwe muti \"Rwose isezerano rya Allah ni ukuri, kandi ko imperuka idashidikanywaho; muravuga muti \"Ntituzi imperuka icyo ari cyo kandi icyo dukora ni ugukeka gusa, ndetse nta n’ubwo twakwemeza (ko uwo munsi uzabaho)"
  45,33,"Kandi ibibi by’ibyo bakoze bizabagaragarira, ndetse bazanagerwaho (n’ibihano) by’ibyo bajyaga bakerensa"
  45,34,"Bazanabwirwa bati \"Uyu munsi turabibagirwa nk’uko mwibagiwe guhura n’uyu munsi wanyu. Ndetse n’ubuturo bwanyu ni umuriro (wa Jahanamu), kandi ntimuzagira ababatabara"
  45,35,"Ibyo (bibabayeho) ni ukubera ko mwakerensaga amagambo ya Allah ndetse mukanashukwa n’ubuzima bw’isi. Bityo, uyu munsi ntibawukurwamo (umuriro), kandi nta n’ubwo bazasubizwa ku isi (ngo bicuze)"
  45,36,"Bityo, ishimwe n’ikuzo ni ibya Allah, Nyagasani w’ibirere, Nyagasani w’isi, akaba na Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose"
  45,37,"Ni nawe (wenyine) w’ikirenga mu birere n’isi, kandi ni we Munyembaraga uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  46,1,Haa Miim
  46,2,"Ihishurwa ry’iki gitabo (Qur’an) rituruka kwa Allah, Umunyembaraga uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  46,3,"Ntitwaremye ibirere n’isi n’ibiri hagati yabyo bitari ku mpamvu z’ukuri, ndetse binagenerwa igihe ntarengwa (bizabaho). Nyamara babandi bahakanye, ibyo baburirwa barabyirengagiza"
  46,4,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Nimunyereke icyo ibyo musenga bitari Allah byaremye ku isi? Ese byaba byaragize uruhare mu iremwa ry’ibirere? Ngaho nimunzanire igitabo cyahishuwe mbere y’iki (Qur’an) cyangwa ibisigisigi by’ubumenyi (bigaragaza ukuri kw’ibyo musenga), niba koko muri abanyakuri"
  46,5,"Ni nde wayobye kurusha wawundi usenga ibitari Allah, bitanashobora kumusubiza kuzageza ku munsi w’imperuka? Ndetse bikaba bitanamenya ko babisaba"
  46,6,"N’igihe abantu bazakoranywa (ku munsi w’imperuka, ibyo basenga) bizababera abanzi, ndetse binabihakane"
  46,7,"N’iyo basomewe amagambo yacu asobanutse, babandi bahakanye igihe ukuri (Qur’an) kubagezeho baravuga bati \"Ubu ni uburozi bugaragara"
  46,8,"Cyangwa bakavuga ko (Muhamadi) yayihimbye (Qur’an)! Vuga uti \"Niba narayihimbye, ntacyo mwamarira kuri Allah. Niweuzi neza ibyo muyinenga. (Allah) arahagije kuba umuhamya hagati yanjye na mwe, kandi ni Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimbabazi"
  46,9,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ntabwo ndi icyaduka mu ntumwa (za Allah), ndetse sinamenya ibyo nzakorerwa cyangwa se ibyo muzakorerwa. Nkurikira ibyo nahishuriwe gusa, kandi ntacyo ndi cyo uretse kuba umuburizi ugaragara"
  46,10,"Vuga uti \"Nimumbwire! Ese niba (Qur’an) ituruka kwa Allah, mwe mukaba muyihakana nyamara umwe muri bene Isiraheli127 ahamya ko (ari ukuri) nka (Tawurati) akaba anayemera mu gihe mwe mwishyira hejuru (muyihakana)\". Mu by’ukuri, Allah ntayobora abantu b’abahakanyi"
  46,11,"Na babandi bahakanye babwiye abemeye bati \"Iyo (ubutumwa bwa Muhamadi) buza kuba ari bwiza, (ababwemeye) ntibari kudutanga kubwemera\". Hanyuma iyo batemeye ko (ubwo butumwa) bubayobora baravuga bati \"iki ni ikinyoma gishaje"
  46,12,"Na mbere yayo (Qur’an) hari igitabo cya Musa (Tawurat) cyari ubuyobozi n’impuhwe. Naho iki (igitabo cya Qur’an) ni ibyakibanjirije, igitabo kiri mu gihamya rurimi rw’Icyarabu, kigamije kuburira inkozi zibibi no gutanga inkuru nziza ku bakora ibyiza"
  46,13,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bavuze bati \"Nyagasani wacu ni Allah, hanyuma bagashikama (ku kuri), nta bwoba ndetse nta n’agahinda bazigera bagira"
  46,14,"Abo ni abantu bo mu Ijuru, bazaribamo ubuziraherezo nk’ingororano z’ibyo bajyaga bakora"
  46,15,"Twanategetse umuntu kugirira neza ababyeyi be. Nyina yamutwitanye umuruho wiyongera ku wundi; kumutwita no kumucutsa mu gihe kingana n’amezi mirongo itatu, kugeza ubwo agera mu gihe cy’ubukure akanagera ku myaka mirongo ine; maze akavuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye! Nshoboza gushimira ingabire zawe wampundagajeho, njye n’ababyeyi banjye, (unanshoboze) gukora ibitunganye wishimira, kandi unantunganyirize urubyaro. Mu by’ukuri, nkwicujijeho kandi rwose ndi mu bicisha bugufi (Abayisilamu)"
  46,16,Abo ni bo twakirira ibyiza bakora tukanirengagiza ibibi byabo. (Bazaba ari) abantu bo mu Ijuru ku bw’isezerano ry’ukuri basezeranyijwe
  46,17,"Ariko wawundi wabwiye ababyeyi be amagambo yo kubinuba (ubwo bamuhamagariraga kwemera Allah n’izuka) agira ati \"Ese muransezeranya ko nzazurwa mu gihe hari ibisekuru byahise mbere yanjye (bitigeze bizurwa)? Mu gihe (ababyeyi be) bitabaza Allah bamubwira bati \"Nya korama! Emera! Rwose isezerano rya Allah ni ukuri\". Ariko we akavuga ati \"Ibi nta kindi biricyo usibye ko ari inkuru z’abo hambere"
  46,18,"Abo ni bo bahamwe n’ijambo (ry’ibihano) nk’iryahamye amajini n’abantu babayeho mbere yabo. Mu by’ukuri, ni abanyagihombo"
  46,19,"Kandi bose bafite inzego (bazahemberwa) bitewe n’ibyo bakoze, kugira ngo (Allah) azabagororere ingororano zabo zuzuye kubera ibikorwa byabo. Kandi ntibazigera bahuguzwa"
  46,20,"Uzirikane n’umunsi babandi bahakanye bazagezwa imbere y’umuriro, maze (babwirwe) bati \"Mwapfushije ubusa ibyiza byanyu mu buzima bw’isi mubyinezezamo. Uyu munsi murahanishwa ibihano bisuzuguritse kubera uko mwajyaga mwibona ku isi bitari mu kuri, no kubera ko mwajyaga mwigomeka (ku mategeko ya Allah)"
  46,21,"Unibuke (yewe Muhamadi) umuvandimwe wa ba Adi (Hudu) ubwo yaburiraga abantu be bari batuye Ah’qaf -kandi bari baraburiwe mbere ye na nyuma ye- avuga ati \"Ntimukagire undi musenga utari Allah. Mu by’ukuri, ndatinya ko muzabona ibihano byo ku munsi uhambaye (nimukomeza guhakana)"
  46,22,"Baravuga bati \"Ese uje kudukura ku mana zacu? (Turabyanze!) Ngaho tuzanire ibyo udusezeranya (ibihano) niba koko uri umwe mu banyakuri"
  46,23,"(Hudu) aravuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, ubumenyi (bw’ibyo bihano) buri kwa Allah. Kandi ibyo mbagezaho n’ibyo natumwe, ariko rwose mbona muri abantu b’injiji"
  46,24,"Maze babonye (igicu cy’ibihano) gikwiriye mu kirere kigana mu bibaya byabo (bari batuyemo, baracyishimira) maze baravuga bati \"Iki gicu kiraduha imvura\". (Hudu) arababwira ati \"Ahubwo ni ibyo mwasabaga kwihutishwa. Ni umuyaga urimo ibihano bibabaza"
  46,25,Urimbura buri kintu cyose (uhuye nacyo) ku bw’itegeko rya Nyagasani wawo. Nuko bucya nta kindi kigaragara usibye amatongo yabo. Uko ni ko duhana abantu b’inkozi z’ibibi
  46,26,"Kandi rwose (aba Adi) twabahaye ubutware tutigeze tubaha mwebwe (Abakurayishi). Tunabaha amatwi, amaso n’imitima (kugira ngo batekereze), nyamara amatwi yabo n’amaso yabo ndetse n’imitima yabo, ntacyo byabamariye kubera ko bahakanaga amagambo ya Allah. Bazagotwa (n’ibihano) by’ibyo bakerensaga"
  46,27,"Kandi rwose (nyuma y’iyo midugudu y’aba Adi), twarimbuye imidugudu ibakikije (yemwe bantu ba Maka), kandi (twakomeje) kubagaragariza ibitangaza kugira ngo bisubireho (ariko baranangira)"
  46,28,Ese izo mana zabo basengaga mu cyimbo cya Allah (bibwira ko) zabamwegereza zaba zarabatabaye? Ahubwo zarabatengushye (mu gihe bahanwaga). Ibyo ni (ingaruka z)’ikinyoma cyabo ndetse n’iz’ibyo bahimbaga
  46,29,"Unibuke (yewe Muhamadi) ubwo twakohererezaga itsinda ry’amajini kugira ngo ryumve Quran, ubwo yahageraga yaravuze ati \"Nimuceceke\". Nuko imaze (gusomwa), (amajini) asubira kuburira bene wayo"
  46,30,"Aravuga ati \"Yemwe bagenzi bacu! Rwose twumvise igitabo cyahishuwe nyuma ya Musa, cyemeza ibyabaye ndetse kiyobora ku kuri no mu nzira igororotse"
  46,31,"Yemwe bagenzi bacu! Nimwumvire intumwa ya Allah (ibyo ibahamagarira), kandi munayemere. (Allah) azababarira ibyaha byanyu anabarinde ibihano bibabaza"
  46,32,"Kandi na wawundi utazumvira intumwa ya Allah, ntabwo ananiye (Allah kuba yamuhana akiri) ku isi. Kandi nta bandi barinzi azagira mu cyimbo cya (Allah). Abo bari mu buyobe bugaragara"
  46,33,"Ese ntibabona ko Allah waremye ibirere n’isi akaba atarananijwe no kubirema, ko ari we ushobora guha ubuzima ibyapfuye? Yego! Rwose ni we ufite ubushobozi kuri buri kintu"
  46,34,"Uzirikane n’umunsi babandi bahakanye bazagezwa imbere y’umuriro, maze (babwirwe) bati \"Ese ibi (ibihano murimo) si ukuri?\" Bavuge bati \"Ni ukuri, turahiye ku izina rya Nyagasani wacu\". (Allah) ababwire ati \"Ngaho nimwumve ububabare bw’ibihano kubera ubuhakanyi bwanyu"
  46,35,"Bityo, ihangane (yewe Muhamadi) nk’uko intumwa zari zifite umuhate zihanganye. Ntuzihutire kubasabira (ibihano). Umunsi bazabona ibyo basezeranyijwe (ibihano), bazaba nk’aho nta gihe bamaze ku isi usibye isaha imwe y’amanywa. Ibi (mubwiwe) ni ubutumwa (mugejejweho). Ese hari abandi bakorekwa uretse abantu b’inkozi z’ibibi"
  47,1,"Babandi bahakanye (Allah n’ubutumwa bw’intumwa Muhamadi), ndetse bakanakumira (abantu) kugana inzira ya Allah, (Allah) azaburizamo ibikorwa byabo"
  47,2,"Naho babandi bemeye (Allah) bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, ndetse bakanemera ibyahishuriwe (Intumwa) Muhamadi; kuko ari ukuri guturutse kwa Nyagasani wabo, (Allah) azabahanaguraho ibyaha anabatu- nganyirize imibereho"
  47,3,"Ibyo ni ukubera ko abahakanyi bakurikiye ikinyoma, naho abemeye bakurikira ukuri guturutse kwa Nyagasani wabo. Uko ni ko Allah aha abantu ingero zabo"
  47,4,"Nimuramuka muhuye na babandi bahakanye (ku rugamba rugamije guhesha Allah icyubahiro), mujye mubakubita ku bikanu. Nimubanesha, mujye mubagira imbohe kugeza intambara irangiye. Hanyuma intambara nirangira, muzabarekure (ntacyo batanze) cyangwa batange inshungu. N’iyo Allah aza kubishaka, yari kubatsinda (nta ruhare mubigizemo); ariko (ibyo yabikoze) kugira ngo agerageze bamwe muri mwe akoresheje abandi. Naho babandi bishwe mu nzira ya Allah, ntazigera aburizamo ibikorwa byabo"
  47,5,Azabayobora anatunganye imibereho yabo
  47,6,Maze anabinjize mu ijuru yabamenyesheje
  47,7,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimuharanira inzira ya Allah, azabatabara anabakomereze igihagararo"
  47,8,"Naho babandi bahakanye, bazarimbuka kandi ibikorwa byabo (Allah) abigire impfabusa"
  47,9,"Ibyo ni ukubera ko bahakanye ibyo Allah yahishuye (Quran), maze nawe akaburizamo ibikorwa byabo"
  47,10,"Ese (abahakanyi) ntibatambagira isi ngo barebe uko iherezo ry’abababanjirije ryagenze? Allah yarabarimbuye, kandi abahakanyi bazabona (iherezo) nka ryo"
  47,11,"Ibyo ni ibigaragaza ko Allah ari inshuti magara y’abemeramana, kandi ko abahakanyi nta nshuti magara bazagira"
  47,12,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, Allah azabinjiza mu busitani butembamo imigezi (Ijuru). Ariko babandi bahakanye, binezeza (kuri iyi si by’igihe gito), maze bakarya nk’uko amatungo arisha (badatekereza ku iherezo ryabo); nyamara umuriro ni wo uzaba ubuturo bwabo"
  47,13,Ese ni imidugudu ingahe yarushaga imbaraga umudugudu wawe (wa Maka) wakumenesheje; nyamara tukaba twarayoretse? Nta n’umutabazi yigeze ibona
  47,14,"Ese babandi bashingiye ku bimenyetso bigaragara biturutse kwa Nyagasani wabo, bamera kimwe nka babandi (Shitani) yakundishije ububi bw’ibikorwa byabo, ndetse bakanakurikira irari ryabo"
  47,15,"Imiterere y’Ijuru ryasezeranyijwe abatinya Allah (ni uko) ritembamo imigezi y’amazi adahindura impumuro n’uburyohe, imigezi y’amata atajya ahindura uburyohe, imigezi y’inzoga ziryoheye abanywi (zidasindisha), ndetse n’imigezi y’ubuki busukuye; kandi bateganyirijwemo buri bwoko bw’imbuto no kubabarirwa na Nyagasani wabo. Ese abo bameze kimwe nk’abazaba mu muriro ubuziraherezo, bahabwa amazi yatuye abacagagura amara"
  47,16,"No muri bo hari abagutega amatwi (yewe Muhamadi), maze mwatandukana bakabwira abahawe ubumenyi bati \"Yahoze avuga iki?\" Abo ni babandi Allah yadanangiye imitima yabo, ndetse banakurikiye irari ryabo"
  47,17,"Naho babandi bayobotse, (Allah) abongerera ukuyoboka ndetse akanabaha ugutinya"
  47,18,Ese (abahakanyi) hari ikindi bategereje kitari ukugerwaho n’imperuka ibaguye gitumo? Nyamara ibimenyetso byayo byamaze gusohora; ese kwibuka byabamarira iki (imperuka) yamaze kubageraho
  47,19,"Bityo, (yewe Muhamadi) menya ko nta yindi mana ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri uretse Allah, unasabe imbabazi z’ibyaha byawe, ndetse (n’ibyaha) by’abemeramana n’abemeramanakazi. Kandi Allah azi neza ibyo mukora (ku manywa) ndetse (n’ibyo mukora nijoro) aho mutuye"
  47,20,"(Kubera ihohoterwa bakorerwaga), babandi bemeye baravuze bati \"Kuki tudahishurirwa isura [(igice cya Qur’an) (iduha uburenganzira bwo kurwanya abaduhohotera)]?\" Ariko iyo isura ihishuwe (igira ibyo isobanura cyangwa itegeka) hakavugwamo imirwano, ubona babandi bafite uburwayi mu mitima yabo bakureba indoro isa nk’iy’uwagushijwe igihumure n’urupfu. Nyamara icyangombwa kuri bo"
  47,21,"Ni ukumvira (Allah) no kuvuga imvugo nziza. Nyamara biramutse bibaye ngombwa (ko bajya ku rugamba), hanyuma bakaba abanyakuri (mubyo basezeranyije) Allah, ni byo byaba ari byiza kuri bo"
  47,22,"Nonese muramutse muteye umugongo (mukanga kumvira Allah n’intumwa ye), ntimwaba abangizi ku isi ndetse mugaca n’imiryango yanyu"
  47,23,"Abo ni bo Allah yavumye, abagira ibipfamatwi ndetse anabahuma amaso"
  47,24,Ese ntibatekereza kuri Qur’an? Cyangwa imitima yabo iradanangiye (ntibasha kumva ukuri)
  47,25,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bahindukiye bagatera umugongo (ukwemera), nyuma y’uko basobanukiwe umuyoboro w’ukuri, Shitani yabakundishije (ibikorwa byabo bibi) inabizeza kubaho igihe kirekire"
  47,26,"(Uko kubizeza kubaho igihe kirekire) ni ukubera ko babwiye abanze ibyo Allah yahishuye (Abayahudi) bati \"Tuzajya tubumvira ku bintu bimwe na bimwe gusa\". Nyamara Allah azi neza amabanga yabo"
  47,27,"Bizaba bimeze bite ubwo abamalayika bazabakuramo roho, babakubita mu buranga bwabo no mu migongo yabo"
  47,28,"Ibyo (bizaba bitewe) n’uko bakurikiye ibirakaza Allah bakanga ibimushimisha, maze ibikorwa byabo akabigira impfabusa"
  47,29,Ese babandi bafite uburwayi (bw’uburyarya) mu mitima yabo bibwira ko Allah atazigera agaragaza inzika zabo (bafitiye intumwa n’abemeramana)
  47,30,"Kandi tubishatse twabakwereka ukababwirwa n’ibimenyetso byabo, ndetse ukanababwirwa no kugobeka imvugo (kwabo). Nyamara Allah azi neza ibikorwa byanyu"
  47,31,"Kandi rwose tuzabagerageza kugeza ubwo tumenye abaharanira inzira y’ukuri n’abihangana muri mwe, ndetse tuzanagaragaza ibikorwa byanyu (byose)"
  47,32,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bahakanye bakanakumira (abantu) kugana inzira ya Allah, ndetse bakananyuranya n’intumwa (Muhamadi) nyuma y’uko basobanukiwe umuyoboro w’ukuri, ntacyo bazatwara Allah. Kandi ibikorwa byabo azabigira impfabusa"
  47,33,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimwumvire Allah, munumvire intumwa (Muhamadi). Kandi ibikorwa byanyu ntimukabigire impfabusa"
  47,34,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bahakanye bakanakumira (abantu) kugana inzira ya Allah, maze bagapfa ari abahakanyi, Allah ntazigera abababarira"
  47,35,"Bityo, ntimuzacike intege (ngo mugire ubwoba) maze ngo mugahamagarire (abanzi banyu) guhagarika intambara kandi ari mwe muri hejuru (mufite intsinzi), kandi Allah ari kumwe namwe ndetse ntazigera agabanya (ibihembo) by’ibikorwa byanyu"
  47,36,"Mu by’ukuri, ubuzima bw’isi nta kindi buri cyo uretse kuba ari umukino no kwinezeza (by’igihe gito). Ariko nimwemera (Allah) mukanamutinya, azabagororera ibihembo byanyu kandi ntazigera abasaba imitungo yanyu"
  47,37,"Aramutse anayibasabye akabatitiriza, mwagira ubugugu (bwo kuyimuha), maze akagaragaza urwango rwanyu (mu kwanga kuyitanga)"
  47,38,"Dore (yemwe bemeramana) ni mwe muhamagarirwa gutanga mu nzira ya Allah, nyamara muri mwe hari abashobora kugira ubugugu. Kandi uzagira ubugugu azaba yihemukiye. Ariko Allah ni we mukungu naho mwe muri abatindi. Kandi nimuramuka mwanze (gutanga mu nzira ya Allah), azabakuraho abasimbuze abandi batari mwe, hanyuma ntibabe nka mwe"
  48,1,"Mu by’ukuri, (yewe Muhamadi) twaguhaye intsinzi igaragara"
  48,2,"Kugira ngo Allah akubabarire ibyaha byawe byabanje n’ibizaza, ndetse anagusenderezeho ingabire ze kandi anakuyobore inzira igororotse"
  48,3,Ndetse no kugira ngo Allah aguhe ubutabazi bukomeye
  48,4,"Ni we wamanuye ituze mu mitima y’abemeramana kugira ngo ukwemera kwabo kwiyongere k’ukwemera basanganywe. Ndetse ingabo zo mu birere no ku isi ni iza Allah, kandi Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  48,5,"Kugira ngo yinjize abemeramana n’abemeramanakazi mu busitani butembamo imigezi (Ijuru) bazabamo ubuziraherezo, ndetse anabababarire ibyaha byabo. Kandi ibyo ni intsinzi ihambaye kwa Allah"
  48,6,"No kugira ngo ahane indyarya z’abagabo n’indyarya z’abagore, ndetse n’ababangikanyamana b’abagabo n’ababangikanyamana b’abagore, bagira ibitekerezo bibi kuri Allah. Amakuba nabe kuri bo! Kandi Allah yarabarakariye, ndetse arabavuma anabateganyiriza umuriro wa Jahanamu, kandi ni wo garukiro ribi"
  48,7,"Ingabo zo mu birere no ku isi ni iza Allah. Kandi Allah ni Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Ushishoza"
  48,8,"Mu by’ukuri, (yewe Muhamadi) twakohereje kugira ngo ube umuhamya, utanga inkuru nziza, kandi unabe umuburizi"
  48,9,"Kugira ngo (yemwe bantu) mwemere Allah n’Intumwa ye, no kugira ngo mumutere inkunga kandi munasingize (Allah) mu gitondo na nimugoroba"
  48,10,"Mu by’ukuri, abagushyigikiye (yewe Muhamadi) baba bashyigikiye Allah. Ukuboko kwa Allah kuri hejuru y’amaboko yabo. Bityo, uzatatira igihango cye, azaba yihemukiye. Kandi uzuzuza ibyo yasezeranyije Allah, azamuha ibihembo bihambaye"
  48,11,"Bamwe mu Barabu bo mu cyaro banze kujya ku rugamba, bazakubwira bati \"Twahugijwe n’imitungo yacu ndetse n’imiryango yacu, bityo dusabire imbabazi.\" Bavugisha indimi zabo ibitari mu mitima yabo. Vuga uti \"Ese ni nde wagira icyo abamarira kwa Allah, aramutse ashatse kubateza ikibi cyangwa ashatse kubagirira neza?\" Ahubwo Allah azi neza ibyo mukora"
  48,12,"Ahubwo mwaketse ko Intumwa ndetse n’abemera batazagaruka mu miryango yabo, nuko ibyo bikundishwa imitima yanyu, maze mugira ibitekerezo bibi, muba abantu boramye"
  48,13,"Naho wawundi utemera Allah n’Intumwa ye (uwo azaba abaye umuhakanyi), kandi rwose twateganyirije abahakanyi umuriro ugurumana"
  48,14,"Kandi ubwami bw’ibirere n’ubw’isi ni ubwa Allah. Ababarira uwo ashatse akanahana uwo ashatse. Kandi Allah ni Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimbabazi"
  48,15,"Nimujya gufata iminyago, abanze kujya ku rugamba bazavuga bati \"Reka tubakurikire.\" Barashaka guhindura amagambo ya Allah. Vuga \"Ntimudukurikire; uko ni ko Allah uti yavuze mbere.\" Hanyuma bazavuga bati \"Ahubwo mwatugiriye ishyari.\" Nyamara ntabwo bari basobanukiwe (ku bya Allah) uretse bike"
  48,16,"Bwira bamwe mu Barabu bo mu cyaro banze kujya ku rugamba uti \"Muzahamagarirwa kujya kurwana n’abantu bafite imbaraga zihambaye; muzarwana na bo cyangwa bishyire mu maboko yanyu (nta mirwano ibayeho). Nimuramuka mwumviye Allah, azabaha ibihembo byiza, ariko nimutera umugongo nk’uko mwabigenje mbere, (Allah) azabahanisha ibihano bibabaza"
  48,17,"Abafite ubumuga bwo kutabona n’abamugaye amaguru, ndetse n’abafite uburwayi ubwo ari bwo bwose, nta mugayo bazabarwaho cyangwa (igihe batagiye icyaha ku rugamba). Bityo, uzumvira Allah n’Intumwa ye, azamwinjiza mu busitani butembamo imigezi (Ijuru); naho uzatera umugongo, (Allah) azamuhanisha ibihano bibabaza"
  48,18,"Mu by’ukuri, Allah yishimiye abemeramana ubwo bagushyigikiraga (yewe Muhamadi) munsi y’igiti. (Allah) yari azi ibiri mu mitima yabo, nuko abamanurira ituze, anabahemba intsinzi ya bugufi"
  48,19,"Ndetse n’iminyago myinshi bazanyaga. Kandi Allah ni Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Ushishoza"
  48,20,"(Allah yabasezeranyije kuzanyaga iminyago myinshi, kandi arabibihutishiriza, ndetse abarinda amaboko y’abantu kubagirira nabi); (bashakaga kugira ngo bibe ikimenyetso ku bemeramana, no kugira ngo abayobore mu nzira igororotse)"
  48,21,"N’indi (minyago) mutashoboye kugeraho, Allah arayibazigamiye. Kandi Allah ni Ushobora byose"
  48,22,"N’iyo abahakanyi baza kubarwanya, bari kubatera umugongo (bahunga), kandi ntibari kubona umurinzi cyangwa umutabazi"
  48,23,Uwo wari umugenzo wa Allah (wo gutabara ingabo ze) ku babayeho mbere. Kandi ntuzigera ubona impinduka ku migenzereze ya Allah
  48,24,"Ni we wabarinze amaboko yabo (ntibabarwanya), ndetse n’amaboko yanyu (ntimwabarwanya) mu kibaya cya Maka (Hudaybiyat) nyuma y’aho ababatsindishije. Kandi Allah ni Ubona bihebuje ibyo mukora"
  48,25,"Abo ni bo bahakanye bakanabakumira kugana Umusigiti Mutagatifu (w’i Maka), ndetse bakanafatira amatungo gutangwaho ibitambo ntagere aho yari yagenewe gutambirwa. Iyo hataba abemeramana b’abagabo n’abemeramana b’abagore (bari mu banzi banyu mwari muhanganye) mutari muzi, mwari kubica cyangwa mukabahutaza mutabizi; bityo mukabarwaho icyaha mutagambiriye gukora. (Ibyo byabayeho) kugira ngo Allah agirire impuhwe uwo ashatse. Kandi n’iyo (abemeramana) baza gutandukana (n’abahakanyi), abahakanye muri bo twari kubahanisha ibihano bibabaza"
  48,26,"Ubwo abahakanye bashyiraga ubwibone mu mitima yabo; ubwibone bwo mu bihe by’ubujiji (kugira ngo batemera ubutumwa bwa Muhamadi), nuko Allah akamanurira ituze ku Ntumwa ye n’abemeramana, abategeka kuguma ku ijambo ryo gutinya Imana; kandi bari barikwiye ndetse ari nabo ba nyiraryo. Allah ni Umumenyi wa buri kintu"
  48,27,"Mu by’ukuri, Allah yagize ukuri inzozi z’Intumwa ye (Muhamadi). Rwose Allah nabishaka, muzinjira mu musigiti mutagatifu wa Maka mutekanye, nta bwoba mufite; (bamwe) mwogoshe imitwe yanyu (abandi) mugabanyije (imisatsi, nk’uko bikorwa mu mutambagiro mutagatifu). (Allah) yari azi neza ibyo mutari muzi, nuko abibahinduriramo intsinzi ya bugufi"
  48,28,"Ni we wohereje Intumwa ye (Muhamadi) izanye umuyoboro (Qur’an) n’idini by’ukuri, kugira ngo arisumbishe andi madini yose. Kandi Allah arahagije kuba umuhamya"
  48,29,"Muhamadi ni Intumwa ya Allah. Kandi babandi bari kumwe na we, bari inkazi ku bahakanyi (igihe babasagariye), bakaba abanyempuhwe hagati yabo. Ubabona bunamye banubamye (basenga), bashaka ingabire za Allah ndetse no kwishimirwa (nawe). Barangwa n’ikimenyetso kiri mu buranga bwabo (baterwa no kubama basenga). Ibi ni byo bibaranga muri Tawurati. Ariko mu Ivanjili, bagaragazwa nk’ikimera cyasohoye umugondoro wacyo, hanyuma ugakomera maze (amashami yacyo) akagikomeza, kigakura kugeza gihagaze cyemye ku gihimba cyacyo mu buryo bushimisha abahinzi. (Urwo rugero rw’abemera) rugamije kurakaza abahakanyi. Allah yasezeranyije abemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, kuzababarirwa ndetse no kuzagororerwa ibihembo bihambaye"
  49,1,"Yemwe abemeye! Ntimukajye mugira ibyo mufataho ibyemezo mbere ya Allah n’Intumwa ye. Kandi mujye mutinya Allah; mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Uwumva bihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  49,2,"Yemwe abemeye! Ntimukajye murangurura amajwi yanyu ngo muvugiremo Umuhanuzi (Muhamadi) igihe ari kuvuga, kandi ntimukajye muzamura amajwi yanyu igihe muvugana nawe nk’uko mubigenza hagati yanyu; kugira ngo ibikorwa byanyu bitazaba impfabusa mutabizi"
  49,3,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bacisha bugufi amajwi yabo imbere y’Intumwa ya Allah; ni bo Allah yejeje imitima kubera kumutinya. Bazababarirwa banahabwe ibihembo bihambaye"
  49,4,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi baguhamagara (mu ijwi riranguruye) bari inyuma y’urugo (iwawe); abenshi muri bo nta bwenge bagira"
  49,5,"Nyamara iyo baza kwihangana kugeza usohotse ubasanga, byari kuba byiza kuri bo. Allah ni Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimbabazi"
  49,6,"Yemwe abemeye! Inkozi y’ibibi niramuka ibazaniye inkuru, mujye mushishoza kugira ngo mudahohotera abantu mutabizi, maze mukaza kwicuza ibyo mwakoze"
  49,7,"Kandi mumenye ko Intumwa ya Allah iri muri mwe. Iyo iza kubumvira muri byinshi, mwari kuba mu bizazane. Ariko Allah yabakundishije ukwemera anagutaka mu mitima yanyu, abangisha ubuhakanyi n’ubwangizi ndetse no kwigomeka. Abo ni bo bayobotse by’ukuri"
  49,8,"Izo ni ingabire n’inema bya Allah, kandi Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  49,9,"Kandi amatsinda abiri y’abemeramana naramuka ashyamiranye, mujye muyunga, ariko rimwe muri yo niryigomeka, mujye murirwanya kugeza ubwo rigarukiye itegeko rya Allah. Niryisubiraho, mujye mubunga mu butabera mutabogamye. Mu by’ukuri, Allah akunda abatabera"
  49,10,"Mu by’ukuri, abemeramana ni abavandimwe. Bityo, mujye mwunga abavandimwe banyu (igihe bashyamiranye), kandi mutinye Allah kugira ngo mugirirwe impuhwe"
  49,11,"Yemwe abemeye! Ntihakagire abantu basuzugura abandi, kuko hari ubwo (abasuzuguwe) baba ari bo beza kubarusha. Kandi n’abagore ntibagasuzugure abagore bagenzi babo, kuko hari ubwo (abasuzuguwe) baba ari bo beza kubarusha. Ntimugasebanye kandi ntimu- gahimbane amazina mabi (atesha agaciro abandi). Mbega ukuntu ari amazina mabi (kuyita bagenzi banyu) nyuma y’uko mubaye abemera! Kandi babandi baticuza, abo ni bo nkozi z’ibibi"
  49,12,"Yemwe abemeye! Mujye mwirinda kenshi gukeka (bagenzi banyu), kuko rimwe na rimwe gukeka ari icyaha. Kandi ntimukanekane cyangwa ngo musebanye. Ese umwe muri mwe yakwemera kurya inyama y’umuvandimwe we wapfuye?(Ntawabyemera !) Ngaho nimubireke kandi mutinye Allah. Mu by’ ukuri, Allah ni Uwakira bihebuje ukwicuza, Nyirimbabazi"
  49,13,"Yemwe bantu! Twabaremye tubakomoye ku mugabo n’umugore, nuko tubagira amahanga n’amoko (atandukanye) kugira ngo mumenyane. Mu by’ukuri, ubarusha icyubahiro imbere ya Allah ni ubarusha gutinya (Allah). Rwose Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje, Uzi byose"
  49,14,"Abarabu bo mu cyaro baravuze bati \"Twaremeye!\" Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ntimuremera, ahubwo nimuvuge muti twabaye Abayislamu\", kuko ukwemera kutarinjira mu mitima yanyu. Ariko nimwumvira Allah n’Intumwa ye, ntacyo azagabanya mu bikorwa byanyu. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Ubabarira bihebuje, Nyirimbabazi"
  49,15,"Mu by’ukuri, abemera nyabo ni abemeye Allah n’Intumwa ye, hanyuma ntibashidikanye (ku byo bemeye), bakanaharanira inzira ya Allah bakoresheje imitungo yabo n’ubuzima bwabo. Abo ni bo banyakuri"
  49,16,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ese muramenyesha Allah iby’idini ryanyu mu gihe Allah azi ibiri mu birere n’ibiri mu isi, kandi Allah ari Umumenyi uhebuje wa buri kintu"
  49,17,"Barakuratira ko babaye Abayislamu (nk’aho ari wowe bifitiye akamaro)? Vuga uti \"Mwikwibwira ko ubuyisilamu bwanyu (ari njye bufitiye akamaro). Ahubwo Allah ni we wabagiriye ubuntu abayobora mu kwemera niba koko muri abanyakuri"
  49,18,"Mu by’ukuri, Allah azi ibitagaragara byo mu birere no mu isi. Kandi Allah ni Ubona bihebuje ibyo mukora"